msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavno okno &okular;ja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&okular;s Main Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavno okno &okular;ja</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basic Usage"
msgstr "Osnovna uporaba"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opening Files"
msgstr "Odpiranje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open any supported file in &okular;, select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, choose a supported "
"file in the dialog and click <guibutton>Open</guibutton>. Your file should "
"now be displayed in the main window."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti katero koli podprto datoteko v programu &okular;, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>, izberite podprto datoteko v pogovornem oknu in kliknite "
"<guibutton>Odpri </guibutton>. Vaša datoteka bi morala biti zdaj prikazana v "
"glavnem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The new document will be opened in a new tab if the <guilabel>Open new files "
"in tabs</guilabel> option on the <link linkend=\"configgeneral\">General "
"configuration page</link> is checked."
msgstr ""
"Nov dokument bo odprt v novem zavihku, če je označena možnost "
"<guilabel>Odpri nove datoteke v zavihkih</guilabel> na <link linkend="
"\"configgeneral\">strani s splošno konfiguracijo</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can close the tab by clicking with &MMB; on it."
msgstr "Zavihek lahko zaprete tako, da kliknete &MMB; na njem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The previously closed document in a tab can be reopened using the "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo close "
"tab</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Predhodno zaprt dokument v zavihku je mogoče znova odpreti z "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Datoteka </guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Razveljavi zapiranje zavihka</guimenuitem></menuchoice> element "
"menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have already opened files in &okular; before, you can quickly access "
"them by selecting them in the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Open Recent</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Če ste že odprli datoteke v programu &okular; prej lahko do njih hitro "
"dostopate tako, da jih izberete v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Odpri nedavno</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&okular; is the default &kde; application for &PDF; and &PostScript; files, "
"launched when you click with the &LMB; on such a file type in the "
"filemanager. If you want to open any file whose format is supported by "
"&okular; use <menuchoice><guimenu>Open with...</guimenu><guimenuitem>&okular;"
"</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from context menu in the filemanager."
msgstr ""
"&okular; je privzeta &kde; aplikacija za &PDF; in &PostScript; datoteke, ki "
"se zaženejo, ko kliknete z &LMB; na takšno vrsto datoteke v upravitelju "
"datotek. Če želite odpreti katero koli datoteko, katere format podpira "
"&okular; uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Odpri z...</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>&okular;</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> iz kontekstnega "
"menija v upravitelju datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After having a file opened you probably want to read it and therefore "
"navigate through it. Go to the <link linkend=\"navigating\">next section</"
"link> to learn more about this."
msgstr ""
"Ko odprete datoteko, jo boste verjetno želeli prebrati in zato krmariti po "
"njej. Pojdite na <link linkend=\"navigating\">naslednji razdelek</link>, če "
"želite izvedeti več o tem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigating"
msgstr "Navigacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section describes how you can navigate through a document in &okular;."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek opisuje, kako lahko krmarite po dokumentu v programu &okular;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are multiple ways of scrolling the viewing area. One is to use the "
"&Up; and &Down; arrow keys. You may also use the scrollbar, your mousewheel "
"or the &PgUp; and &PgDn; keys."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja več načinov premikanja po območju gledanja. Ena je uporaba gor in "
"dol smernih tipk. Uporabite lahko tudi drsni trak, kolesce miške ali &PgUp; "
"in &PgDn; tipki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use <application>vim</application>-like navigation keys, namely "
"<keycap>H</keycap> to move to the top of the previous page, <keycap>L</"
"keycap> to move to the top of the next page, <keycap>J</keycap> to move one "
"line down, and <keycap>K</keycap> to move one line up."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko tudi navigacijske tipke, podobne <application>vim</"
"application>, in sicer <keycap>H</keycap> za pomik na vrh prejšnje strani, "
"<keycap>L</keycap> za pomik na vrh naslednjo stran, <keycap>J</keycap> za "
"premik eno vrstico navzdol in <keycap>K</keycap> za premik eno vrstico "
"navzgor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way is to hold the &LMB; down at any place on the document while "
"dragging the mouse in the opposite direction of where you want to move. This "
"procedure only works if the Browse tool is enabled, which you can select by "
"choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Browse</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Drug način je, da držite &LMB; navzdol na poljubnem mestu v dokumentu, "
"medtem ko miško vlečete v nasprotni smeri, kamor se želite premakniti. Ta "
"postopek deluje le, če je omogočeno orodje za brskanje, ki ga lahko izberete "
"tako, da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Brskaj</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When viewing a document in the <link linkend=\"presentationMode"
"\">Presentation mode</link> use &Up; and &Down; arrow keys to switch between "
"pages or slides. The number and the position of the current slide will be "
"shown in the overlay at the right upper corner of screen."
msgstr ""
"Pri ogledu dokumenta v <link linkend=\"presentationMode\">predstavitvenem "
"načinu</link> uporabite gor in dol puščične tipke za preklapljanje med "
"stranmi ali diapozitivi. Številka in položaj trenutnega diapozitiva bosta "
"prikazana v oknu v desnem zgornjem kotu zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to read a document with several pages use the automatic "
"scrolling feature of &okular;. Start automatic scrolling with <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Down;</keycombo> or <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Shift;&Up;</keycombo>. Then use these keys to increase and decrease the "
"scrolling speed. You can start or stop automatic scrolling temporarily by "
"pressing the &Shift; key; pressing any other key deactivates this feature."
msgstr ""
"Če želite brati dokument z več stranmi, uporabite funkcijo samodejnega "
"drsenja programa &okular;. Zaženite samodejno drsenje s <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;&Down;</keycombo> ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Up;"
"</keycombo>. Nato uporabite te tipke za povečanje in zmanjšanje hitrosti "
"drsenja. Samodejno drsenje lahko začasno zaženete ali ustavite tako, da "
"pritisnete &Shift; ključ; s pritiskom katere koli druge tipke to funkcijo "
"deaktivirate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way to navigate through a document with several pages is to use the "
"mouse pointer. Drag the page up or down, continue to drag even while "
"reaching the bottom or top of the screen and behold. Once you cross the "
"border of a page, the mouse cursor appears on top or bottom of the screen "
"again and you can just continue to drag."
msgstr ""
"Drug način za krmarjenje po dokumentu z več stranmi je uporaba kazalca "
"miške. Povlecite stran gor ali dol, nadaljujte z vlečenjem, tudi ko dosežete "
"dno ali vrh zaslona in glejte. Ko prestopite mejo strani, se kazalec miške "
"znova prikaže na vrhu ali dnu zaslona in lahko nadaljujete z vlečenjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sidebar on the left side of the screen enables two more ways of "
"navigating through a document:"
msgstr ""
"Stranska vrstica na levi strani zaslona omogoča še dva načina krmarjenja po "
"dokumentu:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click on a page thumbnail the viewing area will be brought to that "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete sličico strani, se bo območje za ogled preusmerilo na to stran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the document has a table of contents, clicking on a table of contents "
"item will bring the document to the page linked to that item."
msgstr ""
"Če ima dokument kazalo vsebine, se s klikom na element kazala prikaže "
"dokument na strani, ki je povezana s tem elementom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the document has layers, you can control the layers shown by checking or "
"unchecking the items in the <guilabel>Layers</guilabel> list."
msgstr ""
"Če ima dokument plasti, lahko nadzirate prikazane plasti tako, da označite "
"ali počistite elemente na seznamu <guilabel>Sloji</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the document has bookmarks, enable the <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> "
"view and click them to go to the associated page. If bookmarks are not only "
"shown for the current document, you can quickly switch to bookmarks in all "
"recently opened files."
msgstr ""
"Če ima dokument zaznamke, omogočite pogled <guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel> in "
"jih kliknite, da odprete povezano stran. Če zaznamki niso prikazani samo za "
"trenutni dokument, lahko hitro preklopite na zaznamke v vseh nedavno odprtih "
"datotekah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the document has annotations, enable the <guilabel>Annotations</guilabel> "
"view and click the annotations or select them with the &Up; and &Down; arrow "
"keys and press &Enter; to go to the associated page."
msgstr ""
"Če ima dokument opombe, omogočite pogled <guilabel>Opombe</guilabel> in "
"kliknite opombe ali jih izberite s tipkama gor in dol in pritisnite &Enter; "
"da greste na povezano stran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some documents have links. In this case you can click on them and the view "
"will change to the page it links to. If the link is to a web page or some "
"other document the default &kde; handler for that format will be invoked. "
"For example, clicking on a link pointing to <quote>https://www.kde.org</"
"quote> will open the web page in the default &kde;'s web browser."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri dokumenti imajo povezave. V tem primeru jih lahko kliknete in "
"pogled se bo spremenil na stran, na katero vodi povezava. Če je povezava na "
"spletno stran ali kak drug dokument, je privzeti &kde; priklican bo "
"upravljalnik za to obliko. Na primer, s klikom na povezavo, ki kaže na "
"<quote>https://www.kde.org</quote>, se odpre spletna stran v privzetem "
"spletnem brskalniku &kde;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The document internal links work only when <link linkend=\"menutools"
"\">Browse Tool</link> is used."
msgstr ""
"Notranje povezave do dokumenta delujejo le, če je uporabljeno <link linkend="
"\"menutools\">Orodje za brskanje</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, you may use the following functionality to quickly move to "
"specific places in the document:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko uporabite naslednje funkcije za hitro premikanje na "
"določena mesta v dokumentu:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can go to the beginning of the document using <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo> or using <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Beginning of the document</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Na začetek dokumenta se lahko premaknete z <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Domov</keycap></keycombo> ali z <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Začetek dokument</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can go to the end of the document using <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>End</keycap></keycombo> or using <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>End of the document</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Na konec dokumenta se lahko premaknete z <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Konec</keycap></keycombo> ali z <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konec dokumenta</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can go forward in the document using &Space; or &PgDn;. To go to the "
"next page of the document use the <guibutton>Next Page</guibutton> Toolbar "
"button or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Page</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the menubar."
msgstr ""
"V dokumentu se lahko premaknete naprej s pomočjo preslednice ali &PgDn;. Za "
"prehod na naslednjo stran dokumenta uporabite gumb <guibutton>Naslednja "
"stran</guibutton> orodne vrstice ali <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Naslednja stran</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v menijski vrstici ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can go back in the document using &Backspace; or &PgUp;. To go to the "
"previous page of the document use <guibutton>Previous Page</guibutton> "
"Toolbar button or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous "
"Page</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the menubar."
msgstr ""
"V dokument se lahko vrnete nazaj z &Backspace; ali &PgUp;. Za prehod na "
"prejšnjo stran dokumenta uporabite gumb <guibutton>Prejšnja stran</"
"guibutton> v orodni vrstici ali <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prejšnja stran</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can go back to the positions in the document where you came from in a "
"chronological order. Consider &eg; reading the phrase <quote>As shown in "
"[15], …</quote>, and you want to know quickly lookup reference [15]. So you "
"click on it, and &okular; will jump to the list of references. Using "
"<keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;&Left;</keycombo> or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the menubar will "
"bring you back to exactly the position where you came from."
msgstr ""
"Lahko se vrnete na položaje v dokumentu, od koder ste prišli v kronološkem "
"vrstnem redu. Razmislite npr. branje fraze <quote>Kot je prikazano v [15], …"
"</quote>, in želite izvedeti hitro iskanje reference [15]. Torej kliknete "
"nanjo in program &okular; bo skočil na seznam referenc. Z uporabo "
"<keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;&Left;</keycombo> ali <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v menijski vrstici "
"se boste vrnili točno na položaj, kjer od koder si prišel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can go forward in the document after the jumping back as described above "
"using <keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;&Right;</keycombo> or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the menubar."
msgstr ""
"V dokumentu se lahko premaknete naprej po skoku nazaj, kot je opisano "
"zgoraj, z uporabo <keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;&Right;</keycombo> ali <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v "
"menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can go to the next match when searching using <keycap>F3</keycap> or "
"&Enter; (when the focus is on <guilabel>Find</guilabel> text field) keys or "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> menu item or move back to the previous match using "
"<keycombo>&Shift;<keysym>F3</keysym></keycombo> or <keycombo>&Shift;&Enter;</"
"keycombo> (when the focus is on <guilabel>Find</guilabel> text field) keys "
"or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find Previous</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Pri iskanju s <keycap>F3</keycap> ali &Enter; (ko je fokus na besedilnem "
"polju <guilabel>Najdi</guilabel>) tipkami ali <menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči naslednje</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> element "
"menija ali se pomaknite nazaj na prejšnje ujemanje z uporabo tipk "
"<keycombo>&Shift;<keysym>F3</keysym></keycombo> ali <keycombo>&Shift;&Enter;"
"</keycombo> (ko je fokus na besedilnem polju <guilabel>Najdi</guilabel>) ali "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči prejšnji</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> element menija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Presentation Mode"
msgstr "Način predstavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Presentation mode represents another way to view documents in &okular;. "
"It can be enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Presentation</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. It shows the "
"document on a page per page basis. The pages are shown with zoom to page, "
"that means all the page is visible."
msgstr ""
"Predstavitveni način predstavlja drug način za ogled dokumentov v programu "
"&okular;. Omogoči se lahko v <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Predstavitev</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikazuje "
"dokument stran za stranjo. Strani so prikazane s povečavo strani, kar "
"pomeni, da je vidna vsa stran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&PDF; documents can even specify that they are always opened in presentation "
"mode."
msgstr ""
"&PDF; dokumenti lahko celo določijo, da so vedno odprti v predstavitvenem "
"načinu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When in presentation mode, you have an helper bar located on the top of the "
"screen. Just move the mouse cursor to the top of the screen to make it "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste v predstavitvenem načinu, imate na vrhu zaslona vrstico za pomoč. "
"Samo premaknite kazalec miške na vrh zaslona, da se prikaže."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&okular; in Presentation Mode</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&okular; v predstavitvenem načinu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&okular; in Presentation Mode</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&okular; v predstavitvenem načinu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To navigate between pages you may use the &LMB; (next page) and the &RMB; "
"(previous page), the mouse wheel, the arrow icons or the line edit in the "
"top bar, or the keys specified in the <link linkend=\"navigating"
"\">Navigating</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Za krmarjenje med stranmi lahko uporabite &LMB; (naslednja stran) in &RMB; "
"(prejšnja stran), kolesce miške, ikone s puščicami ali urejanje vrstice v "
"zgornji vrstici ali tipke, določene v razdelku <link linkend=\"navigating"
"\">Krmarjenje</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Play/Pause</guilabel> button in the top bar to start playing "
"presentation or pause it, correspondingly."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guilabel>Predvajaj/Zaustavi</guilabel> v zgornji vrstici, da "
"začnete predvajanje predstavitve ali jo ustrezno zaustavite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can exit presentation mode at any time by pressing the &Esc; key or "
"clicking the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> icon in the top bar."
msgstr ""
"Predstavitveni način lahko kadar koli zapustite tako, da pritisnete &Esc; "
"ali kliknite ikono <guiicon>Zapri</guiicon> v zgornji vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also draw on the current page with a pencil. Click on the "
"<guilabel>Toggle Drawing Mode</guilabel> icon in the top bar to enable or "
"disable the possibility to draw in the presentation mode. The drawings are "
"cleared automatically when leaving the presentation mode. You can also click "
"on the <guilabel>Erase Drawings</guilabel> icon to remove the drawings in "
"the current page."
msgstr ""
"Na trenutno stran lahko rišete tudi s svinčnikom. Kliknite ikono "
"<guilabel>Preklop načina risanja</guilabel> v zgornji vrstici, da omogočite "
"ali onemogočite možnost risanja v predstavitvenem načinu. Risbe se samodejno "
"izbrišejo, ko zapustite način predstavitve. Lahko tudi kliknete ikono "
"<guilabel>Izbriši risbe</guilabel>, da odstranite risbe na trenutni strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The presentation mode has support for more than one screen in a multi-"
"monitor configuration. With more than one screen a new button will appear in "
"the top bar, with the icon of a screen: this is a drop down box that allows "
"you to move the presentation to any of the other available screens."
msgstr ""
"Predstavitveni način podpira več kot en zaslon v konfiguraciji z več "
"monitorji. Pri več kot enem zaslonu se bo v zgornji vrstici pojavil nov gumb "
"z ikono zaslona: to je spustno polje, ki vam omogoča, da predstavitev "
"premaknete na katerega koli drugega razpoložljivega zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Presentation mode has some configuration options, you can find their "
"description in the chapter <link linkend=\"configpresentation\">Configuring "
"&okular;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Predstavitveni način ima nekaj konfiguracijskih možnosti, njihov opis "
"najdete v poglavju <link linkend=\"configpresentation\">Konfiguracija "
"&okular;ja</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inverse Search between &latex; Editors and &okular;"
msgstr "Inverzno iskanje med &latex; Urejevalniki in &okular;jem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inverse search is a very useful feature when you are writing a &latex; "
"document yourself. If everything is set up properly, you can click into "
"&okular;'s window with the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button "
"while pressing &Shift;. After that editor loads the &latex; source file and "
"jumps to the proper paragraph."
msgstr ""
"Inverzno iskanje je zelo uporabna funkcija, ko sami pišete &latex; "
"dokumentirajte. Če je vse pravilno nastavljeno, lahko kliknete v okno "
"&okular; z <mousebutton>levo</mousebutton> tipko miške in hkrati pritisnete "
"&Shift;. Po tem urejevalnik naloži izvorno datoteko &latex; in skoči na "
"ustrezen odstavek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inverse search cannot work unless:"
msgstr "Inverzno iskanje ne more delovati, razen če:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "The source file has been compiled successfully."
msgstr "Izvorna datoteka je bila uspešno prevedena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "&okular; knows which editor you would like to use."
msgstr "&okular; ve, kateri urejevalnik želite uporabiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Browse tool has to be enabled, which you can select by choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Browse </guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Omogočeno mora biti orodje za brskanje, ki ga lahko izberete tako, da "
"izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Brskaj </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this feature of &okular;, a left mouse click while pressing &Shift; in "
"the &DVI; or &PDF; document will result in editor opening the corresponding "
"&latex; document and attempt to go to the corresponding line. Remember to "
"tell &okular; to use proper editor, in &okular;'s menu item "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Okular...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (on the page <guimenuitem>Editor</guimenuitem>)."
msgstr ""
"Pri tej funkciji programa &okular; levi klik miške med pritiskom &Shift; v "
"&DVI; ali &PDF; dokumentu bo urednik odprl ustrezen &latex; dokument in "
"poskusil iti v ustrezno vrstico. Ne pozabite povedati &okular;ju za uporabo "
"ustreznega urejevalnika v &okular;-jevem menijskem elementu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj Okular..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (na strani <guimenuitem>Urejevalnik</guimenuitem "
">)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more details on editor configuration please refer to the <link linkend="
"\"configeditor\">corresponding section of this manual</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti o konfiguraciji urejevalnika si oglejte <link linkend="
"\"configeditor\">ustrezen razdelek tega priročnika</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configuring &okular;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracija &okular;ja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configuring editor in &okular;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguriranje urejevalnika v &okular;ju</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Configuring editor in &okular;</para>"
msgstr "<para>Konfiguriranje urejevalnika v &okular;ju</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "&okular; Advanced Features"
msgstr "Napredne funkcije programa &okular;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "Embedded Files"
msgstr "Vgrajene datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the current document has some files embedded in it, when you open it a "
"bar will appear above the page view to notify you about the embedded files."
msgstr ""
"Če ima trenutni dokument vgrajenih nekaj datotek, se bo, ko ga odprete, nad "
"pogledom strani prikazala vrstica, ki vas bo obvestila o vgrajenih datotekah."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The embedded files bar</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vrstica z vgrajenimi datotekami</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The embedded files bar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vrstica z vgrajenimi datotekami</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this case, you can either click on the link in the text of the bar or "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Embedded Files</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to open the embedded files dialog. The dialog "
"allows you to view the embedded files and to extract them."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru lahko bodisi kliknete povezavo v besedilu vrstice ali izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vgrajene datoteke</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da odprete pogovorno okno za vgrajene datoteke. "
"Pogovorno okno vam omogoča ogled vgrajenih datotek in njihovo izvlečenje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forms"
msgstr "Obrazci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the current document has forms, when you open it a bar will appear above "
"the page view where you can enable the forms."
msgstr ""
"Če ima trenutni dokument obrazce, se bo, ko ga odprete, nad pogledom strani "
"pojavila vrstica, kjer lahko omogočite obrazce."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The forms bar</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vrstica z obrazci</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The forms bar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vrstica z obrazci</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this case, you can either click on <guilabel>Show Forms</guilabel> in the "
"bar or choose <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Forms</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to enter data into the form fields."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru lahko kliknete <guilabel>Pokaži obrazce</guilabel> v vrstici "
"ali izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži "
"obrazce</guimenuitem></menuchoice> za vnos podatkov v polja obrazca."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "Signatures"
msgstr "Podpisi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the current document has signatures a bar will appear above the page view "
"after the document opening. It allows you to open the <guilabel>Signatures</"
"guilabel> panel."
msgstr ""
"Če ima trenutni dokument podpise, se bo po odprtju dokumenta nad pogledom "
"strani pojavila vrstica. Omogoča odpiranje plošče <guilabel>Podpisi</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The signatures bar</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vrstica s podpisi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The signatures bar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vrstica s podpisi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the <guilabel>Signatures</guilabel> panel you can inspect the document "
"signature and its certificate."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo plošče <guilabel>Podpisi</guilabel> lahko pregledate podpis "
"dokumenta in njegovo potrdilo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The signatures panel</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Plošče s podpisi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The signatures panel</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Plošče s podpisi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature is available for &PDF; documents only. You need to install at "
"least version 0.51 of <ulink url=\"https://poppler.freedesktop.org/"
"\">Poppler</ulink> to get most signature information, version 0.68 to get "
"signature location/reason information, and version 0.73 to get signature "
"certificate information."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija je na voljo samo za &PDF; dokumente. Za pridobitev večine "
"informacij o podpisih morate namestiti vsaj različico 0.51 programa <ulink "
"url=\"https://poppler.freedesktop.org/\">Poppler</ulink>, različico 0.68 za "
"pridobitev informacij o lokaciji/razlogu podpisa in različico 0.73 za "
"pridobitev informacij o potrdilu o podpisu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Digital Signatures"
msgstr "Dodajanje digitalnih podpisov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add digital signatures to documents using the corresponding action "
"in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Dokumentom lahko dodate digitalne podpise z ustreznim dejanjem v meniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be able to sign a document you need to have a proper <acronym>PKCS</"
"acronym> signing certificate available on your system. &okular; does not "
"have the ability to create such certificates since they need to be issued by "
"certificate authorities to be useful for validation, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Da bi lahko podpisali dokument, morate imeti v sistemu na voljo ustrezno "
"podpisno potrdilo <acronym>PKCS</acronym>. &okular; nima zmožnosti ustvariti "
"takih potrdil, ker jih morajo izdati overitelji potrdil, da so uporabna za "
"preverjanje &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We use the Poppler library to handle signing of &PDF; documents and Poppler "
"is using the NSS library to handle certificates. At the point of writing, "
"Poppler will try to use one of the following NSS certificate stores in order "
"(the first that exists):"
msgstr ""
"Za podpisovanje &PDF; dokumentov uporabljamo knjižnico Poppler, ki uporablja "
"knjižnico NSS za obdelavo potrdil. V trenutku pisanja bo Poppler poskušal "
"uporabiti eno od naslednjih shramb potrdil NSS po vrstnem redu (prvo, ki "
"obstaja):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid "The current Firefox user certificate store."
msgstr "Trenutna shramba uporabniških potrdil Firefox."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "The system-wide <filename>/etc/pki/nssdb</filename> certificate store."
msgstr "Sistemska shramba potrdil <filename>/etc/pki/nssdb</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "The current user <filename>$HOME/.pki/nssdb</filename>"
msgstr "Trenutni uporabnik <filename>$HOME/.pki/nssdb</filename>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to use a custom certificate store you can do so by setting it in "
"the <link linkend=\"config-pdf-digital-signatures\">&PDF; Backend "
"Configuration</link> section of the <link linkend=\"configure-backends"
"\">Configure Backends...</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti shrambo potrdil po meri, lahko to storite tako, da jo "
"nastavite v <link linkend=\"config-pdf-digital-signatures\">&PDF; Razdelku "
"Konfiguracije ozadja</link> pogovornega okna <link linkend=\"configure-"
"backends\">Konfiguriraj ozadja...</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature is available for &PDF; documents only. You need to install at "
"least version 21.01 of <ulink url=\"https://poppler.freedesktop.org/"
"\">Poppler</ulink> to be able to add digital signatures to a document."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija je na voljo za samo &PDF; dokumente. Če želite dokumentu dodati "
"digitalne podpise, morate namestiti vsaj različico 21.01 programa <ulink url="
"\"https://poppler.freedesktop.org/\">Poppler</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:499 index.docbook:2906
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Annotations</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opombe</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "&okular; allows you to review and annotate your documents."
msgstr "&okular; omogoča pregledovanje in komentiranje vaših dokumentov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&okular;'s Annotations</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Okularjeve opombe</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&okular;'s Annotations</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Okularjeve opombe</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "&okular; has two different kind of annotations:"
msgstr "&okular; ima dve različni vrsti opomb:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Text annotations like <guilabel>Yellow Highlighter</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Black Underlining</guilabel> can be used with files containing "
"text (&eg; &PDF;)."
msgstr ""
"Besedilne opombe, kot sta <guilabel>Rumeni označevalec</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Črno podčrtano</guilabel>, lahko uporabite z datotekami, ki "
"vsebujejo besedilo (npr. &PDF;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Graphic annotations like <guilabel>Pop-up Note</guilabel>, <guilabel>Inline "
"Note</guilabel>, <guilabel>Freehand Line</guilabel>, <guilabel>Highlighter</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Straight Line</guilabel>, <guilabel>Polygon</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Stamp</guilabel>, <guilabel>Underline</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Ellipse</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Typewriter</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Grafične opombe, kot so <guilabel>Pojavna opomba</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Vdelana opomba</guilabel>, <guilabel>Prostoročna črta</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Označevalnik</guilabel>, <guilabel>Ravna črta</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Mnogokotnik</guilabel>, <guilabel>Žig</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Podčrtano</guilabel>, <guilabel>Elipsa</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Pisalni stroj</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Graphic annotations are not limited to &PDF; files; they can be used for any "
"format that &okular; supports."
msgstr ""
"Grafične opombe niso omejene na &PDF; datoteke; mogoče jih je uporabiti za "
"kateri koli format, ki ga podpira &okular;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the <guilabel>Annotations</guilabel> menu, you can add a <guilabel>Pop "
"up Note</guilabel> or any other kind of annotation to add or edit comments."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo menija <guilabel>Opombe</guilabel> lahko dodate <guilabel>Pojavno "
"opombo</guilabel> ali katero koli drugo vrsto opombe za dodajanje ali "
"urejanje komentarjev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&okular; has the \"document archiving\" feature. This is an &okular;-"
"specific format for carrying the document plus various metadata related to "
"it (currently only annotations). You can save a \"document archive\" from "
"the open document by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Save As</guisubmenu></menuchoice> and selecting "
"<guilabel>Okular document archive</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Filter</"
"guilabel> selector. Documents saved this way will get <filename>.okular</"
"filename> as their filename extension. To open an &okular; document archive, "
"just open it with &okular; as it would be &eg; a &PDF; document."
msgstr ""
"&okular; ima funkcijo \"arhiviranja dokumentov\". To je format, specifičen "
"za &okular; za prenašanje dokumenta in različnih metapodatkov, povezanih z "
"njim (trenutno samo opombe). Iz odprtega dokumenta lahko shranite »arhiv "
"dokumentov« tako, da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Shrani kot</guisubmenu></menuchoice> in izberete "
"<guilabel>Arhiv dokumentov Okular</guilabel> v izbirniku <guilabel>Filter</"
"guilabel>. Tako shranjeni dokumenti bodo kot pripono imena datoteke dobili "
"<filename>.okular</filename>. Če želite odpreti &okular; arhiv dokumentov, "
"ga odprite z programom &okular; kot bi bil npr. &PDF; dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can <emphasis>also</emphasis> save annotations directly into &PDF; "
"files. You can use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to save it over the current file or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> to save it to a new file."
msgstr ""
"Opombe lahko shranite <emphasis>tudi</emphasis> neposredno v &PDF; datoteke. "
"Uporabite lahko <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da jo shranite nad trenutno datoteko, ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da jo shranite v novo datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that adding, editing, or removing annotations may not be possible with "
"DRM-enabled files."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da dodajanje, urejanje ali odstranjevanje opomb morda ne bo "
"mogoče pri datotekah, ki podpirajo DRM."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to <link linkend=\"edit-undo\">undo</link> or <link linkend="
"\"edit-redo\">redo</link> any annotation action by using the corresponding "
"item from the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu. It is also possible to undo the "
"action by pressing <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> and to redo "
"a previously undone action by pressing <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</"
"keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Možno je <link linkend=\"edit-undo\">razveljaviti</link> ali <link linkend="
"\"edit-redo\">ponoviti</link> katero koli dejanje opombe z uporabo "
"ustreznega elementa v <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> meni. Dejanje je mogoče "
"razveljaviti tudi s pritiskom na <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> in ponoviti predhodno razveljavljeno dejanje s pritiskom na "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap ></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the default properties and appearance of each annotation "
"tool. Please refer to the <link linkend=\"configannotations\">corresponding "
"section in this documentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko privzete lastnosti in videz vsakega orodja za opombe. "
"Oglejte si <link linkend=\"configannotations\">ustrezen razdelek v tej "
"dokumentaciji</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding annotations"
msgstr "Dodajanje opomb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add annotations to the document, you can use <guilabel>Quick Annotations</"
"guilabel> button on the main &okular; toolbar, or activate the annotation "
"toolbar. This is done by either selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Annotations</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or pressing "
"<keycap>F6</keycap>. Once the annotation toolbar is shown, just press one of "
"its buttons or use keyboard shortcuts (keys from <keycap>1</keycap> to "
"<keycap>9</keycap>) to use that annotation."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dokumentu dodati opombe, lahko uporabite gumb <guilabel>Hitre "
"opombe</guilabel> na glavni &okular; orodni vrstici ali aktivirajte orodno "
"vrstico za opombe. To storite tako, da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Opombe</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali pritisnete "
"<keycap>F6</keycap>. Ko se prikaže orodna vrstica za opombe, samo pritisnite "
"enega od njenih gumbov ali uporabite bližnjice na tipkovnici (tipke od "
"<keycap>1</keycap> do <keycap>9</keycap>), da uporabite to opombo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The annotation toolbar helps you to make annotations with drawings, shapes, "
"and text messages. You can use the annotation toolbar to mark up a document "
"(&eg; add lines, ellipses, polygons, stamps, highlights, underlines &etc;). "
"The table below describes exactly what the default set of annotation toolbar "
"buttons does."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica za opombe vam pomaga ustvarjati opombe z risbami, oblikami in "
"besedilnimi sporočili. Z orodno vrstico za opombe lahko označite dokument "
"(npr. dodate črte, elipse, mnogokotnike, žige, poudarke, podčrtaje itd.). "
"Spodnja tabela natančno opisuje, kaj počne privzeti nabor gumbov orodne "
"vrstice za opombe."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:556 index.docbook:973 index.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button"
msgstr "Gumb"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tool Name"
msgstr "Ime orodja"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:562 index.docbook:979 index.docbook:1130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlighter"
msgstr "Označevalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlights text in the document with a given background color."
msgstr "Označi besedilo v dokumentu z dano barvo ozadja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; and drag to highlight a "
"text snippet."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; in povlecite, da označite delček "
"besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Type</guilabel> "
"(<guimenuitem>Highlight</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Squiggle</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Underline</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Strike out</"
"guimenuitem>), <guilabel>Color</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Opacity</guilabel> "
"for the highlighter. Just right-click on the highlighted text and select the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Možno je definirati <guilabel>Vrsto</guilabel> (<guimenuitem>Označi</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Vijugast</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Podčrtaj</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Prečrtaj</guimenuitem >), <guilabel>Barvo</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Prosojnost</guilabel> za označevalnik. Z desno "
"miškino tipko kliknite označeno besedilo in izberite menijsko postavko "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid "Underline"
msgstr "Podčrtaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "Underlines text with a straight line."
msgstr "Besedilo podčrta z ravno črto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:614
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; and drag to underline a "
"text snippet."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; in povlecite, da podčrtate "
"delček besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:617 index.docbook:644 index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Type</guilabel> "
"(<guimenuitem>Highlight</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Squiggle</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Underline</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Strike out</"
"guimenuitem>), <guilabel>Color</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Opacity</guilabel> "
"for the underline. Just right-click on the underlined text and select the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Možno je definirati <guilabel>Vrsto</guilabel> (<guimenuitem>Označi</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Vijugast</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Podčrtaj</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Prečrtaj</guimenuitem >), <guilabel>Barvo</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Prosojnost</guilabel> za podčrtaj. Z desno miškino "
"tipko kliknite podčrtano besedilo in izberite menijsko postavko "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid "Squiggle"
msgstr "Vijuganje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid "Underlines text with a squiggly line."
msgstr "Besedilo podčrta z vijugasto črto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; and drag to squiggly "
"underline a text snippet."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; in povlecite, da vijugasto "
"podčrtate delček besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strike Out"
msgstr "Prečrtati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strikes out some text."
msgstr "Prečrta nekaj besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; and drag to squiggly "
"strike out a text snippet."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; in povlecite, da vijugasto "
"prečrtate delček besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid "Typewriter"
msgstr "Pisalni stroj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds text on a transparent background. This is useful for filling out forms "
"lacking integrated editable text fields."
msgstr ""
"Doda besedilo na prozorno ozadje. To je uporabno za izpolnjevanje obrazcev "
"brez integriranih besedilnih polj, ki jih je mogoče urejati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; where you wish to add "
"the top-left corner of the text, then drag to place the bottom-right one. "
"Type some text, then click on the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to save it, "
"<guibutton>Clear</guibutton> to clear the text and start over, or "
"<guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> to cancel."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; kamor želite dodati zgornji levi "
"kot besedila, nato povlecite, da postavite spodnjega desnega. Vnesite "
"besedilo, nato kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da ga shranite, "
"<guibutton>Počisti</guibutton>, da počistite besedilo in začnete znova, ali "
"<guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>, da prekličete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Font</guilabel> and <guilabel>Text "
"color</guilabel> for the text. Just right-click on the typewriter text "
"created and select the <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Možno je določiti <guilabel>Pisavo</guilabel> in <guilabel>Barvo besedila</"
"guilabel> za besedilo. Z desno miškino tipko kliknite ustvarjeno besedilo "
"pisalnega stroja in izberite menijsko postavko <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inline Note"
msgstr "Opomba v vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws an inline note. The note will be shown inline as is."
msgstr "Nariše opombo v vrstici. Opomba bo prikazana v vrstici, kakršna je."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; where you wish to add "
"the top-left corner of the note, then drag to place the bottom-right one. "
"Enter the text of the note then click on the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to "
"save the note, <guibutton>Clear</guibutton> to clear the note's text, or "
"<guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> to cancel note creation."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; kamor želite dodati zgornji levi "
"kot zapiska, nato povlecite, da postavite spodnjega desnega kota. Vnesite "
"besedilo opombe in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da shranite "
"opombo, <guibutton>Počisti</guibutton>, da počistite besedilo opombe, ali "
"<guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>, da prekličete ustvarjanje opombe ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Color</guilabel>, <guilabel>Opacity</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Font</guilabel>, <guilabel>Align</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>Border width</guilabel> for the note. Just right-click on the note "
"icon created and select the <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Možno je določiti <guilabel>barvo</guilabel>, <guilabel>motnost</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>pisavo</guilabel>, <guilabel>poravnavo</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>širino obrobe</guilabel> za opombo. Z desno miškino tipko kliknite "
"ustvarjeno ikono opombe in izberite menijsko postavko "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pop-up Note"
msgstr "Pojavna opomba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draws a multiline note. The note can be viewed by double clicking on the "
"icon created in the document."
msgstr ""
"Nariše večvrstični zapis. Opombo si lahko ogledate z dvojnim klikom na "
"ikono, ustvarjeno v dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click on the place in the document where the "
"pop-up note should be added. Enter the text of pop-up note then click on the "
"<guilabel>Close this note</guilabel> button in the top right corner of the "
"pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja in nato kliknite mesto v dokumentu, kamor naj bo dodana "
"pojavna opomba. Vnesite besedilo pojavne opombe in kliknite gumb "
"<guilabel>Zapri to opombo</guilabel> v zgornjem desnem kotu pojavnega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Color</guilabel>, <guilabel>Opacity</"
"guilabel>, and <guilabel>Icon</guilabel> for the note. Just right-click on "
"the note icon created and select the <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> "
"menu item."
msgstr ""
"Možno je določiti <guilabel>Barvo</guilabel>, <guilabel>Prosojnost</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Ikono</guilabel> za zapisek. Z desno miškino tipko "
"kliknite ustvarjeno ikono opombe in izberite menijsko postavko "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "Freehand Line"
msgstr "Prostoročna črta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws free-form lines."
msgstr "Riše črte proste oblike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; and drag to draw the "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; in povlecite, da narišete črto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Color</guilabel>, <guilabel>Opacity</"
"guilabel>, and <guilabel>Width</guilabel> for the line. Just right-click on "
"the line created and select the <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Za črto je možno določiti <guilabel>Barvo</guilabel>, <guilabel>Prosojnost</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Širino</guilabel>. Z desno miškino tipko kliknite "
"ustvarjeno vrstico in izberite menijsko postavko <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:795
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow (drop-down list)"
msgstr "Puščica (spustni seznam)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws an arrow between two points."
msgstr "Nariše puščico med dvema točkama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; to place the starting "
"point of the arrow, then drag to place the ending point of the line and "
"click once more."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; da postavite začetno točko "
"puščice, nato povlecite, da postavite končno točko črte, in še enkrat "
"kliknite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:806 index.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Color</guilabel>, <guilabel>Opacity</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Width</guilabel>, <guilabel>Line start</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Line end</guilabel>, <guilabel>Leader line length</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>Leader line extension length</guilabel> for the line. Just right-"
"click on the line created and select the <guimenuitem>Properties</"
"guimenuitem> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Možno je določiti <guilabel>Barvo</guilabel>, <guilabel>Prosojnost</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Širino</guilabel>, <guilabel>Začetek vrstice</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Konec vrstice</guilabel>, <guilabel>Dolžina vodilne "
"črte</guilabel> in <guilabel>Dolžina podaljška vodilne črte</guilabel> za "
"črto desno miškino tipko kliknite ustvarjeno vrstico in izberite menijsko "
"postavko <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
msgid "Straight line (drop-down list)"
msgstr "Ravna črta (spustni seznam)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws a line between two points."
msgstr "Nariše črto med dvema točkama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; to place the starting "
"point of the line, then drag to place the ending point of the line and click "
"once more."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; da postavite začetno točko črte, "
"nato povlecite, da postavite končno točko črte, in še enkrat kliknite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:849
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rectangle (drop-down list)"
msgstr "Pravokotnik (spustni seznam)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:854
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws a rectangle around the chosen area."
msgstr "Okoli izbranega območja nariše pravokotnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; to place the top-left "
"corner of the rectangle, then drag to place the bottom-right one."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; da postavite zgornji levi kot "
"pravokotnika, nato povlecite, da postavite spodnjega desnega kota."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:860 index.docbook:887
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Type</guilabel> "
"(<guimenuitem>Rectangle</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Ellipse</"
"guimenuitem>), <guilabel>Color</guilabel>, <guilabel>Opacity</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Shape fill</guilabel> (and its color), and <guilabel>Width</"
"guilabel> for the border. Just right-click on the border created and select "
"the <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Možno je definirati <guilabel>Vrsto</guilabel> (<guimenuitem>Pravokotnik</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Elipsa</guimenuitem>), <guilabel>Barvo</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Prosojnost</guilabel >, <guilabel>Polnilo oblike</"
"guilabel> (in njegova barva) in <guilabel>Širino</guilabel> za obrobo. Z "
"desno miškino tipko kliknite ustvarjeno obrobo in izberite menijsko postavko "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ellipse (drop-down list)"
msgstr "Elipsa (spustni seznam)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:881
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draws an ellipse or rectangle around a chosen area."
msgstr "Okoli izbranega območja nariše elipso ali pravokotnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; and hold to place the "
"top-left corner of the circumscribed rectangle for the ellipse, then drag to "
"place the bottom-right one."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; in pridržite, da postavite "
"zgornji levi kot obrobljenega pravokotnika za elipso, nato povlecite, da "
"postavite spodnjega desnega kota."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid "Polygon (drop-down list)"
msgstr "Večkotnik (spustni seznam)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draws a closed shape from three or more line segments. The corresponding "
"note can be viewed by double clicking inside the polygon."
msgstr ""
"Nariše zaprto obliko iz treh ali več segmentov črte. Ustrezno opombo si "
"lahko ogledate z dvojnim klikom znotraj večkotnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button, then click with the &LMB; to place the first "
"vertex of the polygon, then drag to place of the second vertex. Proceed "
"until you have drawn the whole polygon and connected back up with the first "
"vertex. Click twice to add a note to the polygon. Enter the text of the note "
"then click on the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to save the note, "
"<guibutton>Clear</guibutton> to clear the note, or <guibutton>Cancel</"
"guibutton> to cancel note entry."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, nato kliknite z &LMB; da postavite prvo oglišče "
"večkotnika, nato povlecite na mesto drugega oglišča. Nadaljujte, dokler ne "
"narišete celotnega večgona in se ponovno povežete s prvo točko. Kliknite "
"dvakrat, da večkotniku dodate opombo. Vnesite besedilo opombe in kliknite "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da shranite opombo, <guibutton>Počisti</"
"guibutton>, da počistite opombo, ali <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>, da "
"prekličete vnos opombe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Color</guilabel>, <guilabel>Opacity</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Shape fill</guilabel> (and its color), and "
"<guilabel>Width</guilabel> for the polygon. Just right-click on the polygon "
"created and select the <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Za večkotnik lahko definirate <guilabel>Barvo</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Prosojnost</guilabel>, <guilabel>Polnilo oblike</guilabel> (in "
"barvo), in <guilabel>Širino</guilabel>. Z desno miškino tipko kliknite "
"ustvarjeni večkotnik in izberite menijsko postavko <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stamp"
msgstr "Žig"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserts a pre-defined shape into the document."
msgstr "V dokument vstavi vnaprej določeno obliko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:938
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the tool button to choose the stamp from the drop-down list then "
"click with the &LMB; to place the stamp."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb orodja, da izberete žig s spustnega seznama, nato kliknite z "
"&LMB; za oddajo žiga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A single click just places a square stamp (useful for icons). To add a "
"rectangular stamp you can click with the &LMB; and hold to place the top-"
"left point, then drag to place the bottom-right one."
msgstr ""
"Z enim klikom samo postavite kvadratni žig (uporabno za ikone). Če želite "
"dodati pravokotni žig, kliknite z &LMB; in pridržite, da postavite zgornjo "
"levo točko, nato povlecite, da postavite spodnjo desno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to define the <guilabel>Opacity</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Stamp symbol</guilabel> for the stamp. Just right-click on the "
"stamp icon created and select the <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Možno je določiti <guilabel>Prosojnost</guilabel> in <guilabel>Simbol žiga</"
"guilabel> za žig. Z desno miškino tipko kliknite ustvarjeno ikono žiga in "
"izberite menijsko postavko <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental. Custom stamps inserted in &PDF; documents are "
"not visible in &PDF; readers other than &okular;."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija je poskusna. Žigi po meri vstavljeni v &PDF; dokumente niso "
"vidni v PDF bralnikih, ki niso okular;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:958
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are the default annotations provided by &okular;. Using the <link "
"linkend=\"configannotations\">Annotations page</link> of the configuration "
"dialog you can add your own annotations like custom stamps, text markup or a "
"geometrical shape with inner color to highlight regions &etc;"
msgstr ""
"To so privzete opombe, ki jih ponuja &okular;. Na <link linkend="
"\"configannotations\">strani z opombami</link> v konfiguracijskem pogovornem "
"oknu lahko dodate lastne opombe, kot so žigi po meri, oznake besedila ali "
"geometrijske oblike z notranjo barvo za označevanje regij &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to add &latex; code into the text of annotations. To do so, "
"add <userinput>$$<replaceable>code</replaceable>$$</userinput> into the text "
"of annotation, where <replaceable>code</replaceable> is any valid &latex; "
"equation. Follow the instructions that will appear on the screen to render "
"it using a &latex; distribution installed in your system."
msgstr ""
"Možno je dodati &latex; kodo v besedilo opomb. Če želite to narediti, "
"dodajte <userinput>$$<replaceable>code</replaceable>$$</userinput> v "
"besedilo opombe, kjer je <replaceable>code</replaceable> katera koli "
"veljavna &latex; enačba. Sledite navodilom, ki se bodo pojavila na zaslonu, "
"da ga upodabljate z &latex; distribucijo nameščeno v vašem sistemu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to configure the selected tool using the annotation toolbar "
"itself:"
msgstr "Izbrano orodje je možno konfigurirati s samo orodno vrstico za opombe:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option Name"
msgstr "Ime možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line width"
msgstr "Širina črte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click on this button to choose the width from the drop-down list."
msgstr "Kliknite na ta gumb, da izberete širino s spustnega seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>/</para>"
msgstr "<para>/</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotation color"
msgstr "Barva pripisa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1028
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on this button to choose the color of the text or border of your "
"annotation. You can chose one of the predefined colors or click on the "
"<guimenuitem>Custom Color...</guimenuitem> item to open the color selection "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na ta gumb, da izberete barvo besedila ali obrobe vaše opombe. "
"Izberete lahko eno od vnaprej določenih barv ali kliknete na element "
"<guimenuitem>Barva po meri...</guimenuitem>, da odprete pogovorno okno za "
"izbiro barve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1044
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotation fill color"
msgstr "Barva polnila pripisov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1049
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on this button to choose the fill color of your annotation. You can "
"chose one of the predefined colors or click on the <guimenuitem>Custom "
"Color...</guimenuitem> item to open the color selection dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na ta gumb, da izberete barvo polnila vaše opombe. Izberete lahko "
"eno od vnaprej določenih barv ali kliknete na element <guimenuitem>Barva po "
"meri...</guimenuitem>, da odprete pogovorno okno za izbiro barve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotation opacity"
msgstr "Neprosojnost opombe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on this button to choose the opacity of your annotation from the drop-"
"down list (<guimenuitem>100%</guimenuitem> creates opaque annotations)."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ta gumb, da izberete prosojnost vaše opombe s spustnega seznama "
"(<guimenuitem>100 %</guimenuitem> ustvari neprozorne opombe)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotation font"
msgstr "Pisava opombe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click on this button to open the font selection dialog."
msgstr "Kliknite na ta gumb, da odprete pogovorno okno za izbiro pisave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced settings for the current annotation tool"
msgstr "Napredne nastavitve za trenutno orodje za opombe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on this button to open the general configuration dialog for your "
"annotation."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ta gumb, da odprete splošno konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno za svojo "
"opombo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are three additional utility buttons on the annotation toolbar:"
msgstr "V orodni vrstici za opombe so trije dodatni pomožni gumbi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the current annotation to the <guilabel>Quick Annotations</guilabel> "
"menu on the main toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte trenutno opombo v meni <guilabel>Hitre opombe</guilabel> v glavni "
"orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the default shortcuts from <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>9</keycap></keycombo> to <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>0</"
"keycap></keycombo> to select the quick annotation actions any time you like, "
"even with the annotation toolbar hidden."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko privzete bližnjice od <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>9</keycap></keycombo> do <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>0</"
"keycap></keycombo>, da kadar koli izberete hitra dejanja pripisov, tudi če "
"je orodna vrstica pripisov skrita."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid "When checked, keep the current annotation tool active after use."
msgstr "Ko je označeno, ohrani trenutno orodje za opombe aktivno po uporabi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide the annotation toolbar."
msgstr "Skrij orodno vrstico za opombe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By pressing &Shift; you can constrain the angle of line and polygon "
"annotations to 15° steps, and the ratio of shape annotations (&eg; "
"Rectangle, Ellipse) to 1:1. You can also get a toolbar button from <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/config.html#toolbars\">Configure Toolbars...</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom na &Shift; lahko omejite kote v večkotnikov na korake po 15°, "
"razmerje pripisov oblik (npr. Pravokotnik, Elipsa) pa na 1:1. Gumb orodne "
"vrstice lahko dobite tudi na <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/config."
"html#toolbars\">Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice...</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents of the <guilabel>Quick Annotations</guilabel> menu can be "
"configured using the <link linkend=\"configannotations\">Annotations page of "
"&okular; configuration dialog</link>. This page can be opened by clicking "
"<guilabel>Quick Annotations</guilabel> button, then choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Annotations...</guimenuitem> from the pop-up menu."
msgstr ""
"Vsebino menija <guilabel>Hitre opombe</guilabel> lahko konfigurirate s "
"pomočjo <link linkend=\"configannotations\">strani z opombami v &okular;"
"jevem konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</link>. To stran lahko odprete tako, "
"da kliknete gumb <guilabel>Hitre opombe</guilabel> in nato v pojavnem meniju "
"izberete <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj opombe...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activating the annotation toolbar will automatically switch to Browse Mode."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviranje orodne vrstice za opombe bo samodejno preklopilo v način "
"brskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can stop annotating any time by pressing the button of the annotation "
"you are using again, or by pressing the &Esc; key."
msgstr ""
"Komentiranje lahko kadar koli prekinete tako, da ponovno pritisnete gumb "
"opombe, ki jo uporabljate, ali pritisnete &Esc; tipko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The newly created annotation will have the author you set in the <link "
"linkend=\"configannotations\"><guilabel>Annotations</guilabel> page</link> "
"in &okular;s configuration dialog as its author. The <guilabel>Annotations</"
"guilabel> page can also be used to configure the content of the annotations "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Novo ustvarjena opomba bo imela avtorja, ki ste ga nastavili na strani <link "
"linkend=\"configannotations\"><guilabel>Opombe</guilabel></link> v "
"konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu &okular;ja. Stran <guilabel>Pripombe</"
"guilabel> lahko uporabite tudi za nastavitev vsebin orodne vrstice pripomb."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removing annotations"
msgstr "Odstranjevanje opomb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove an annotation, first select the Browse tool "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Browse</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>) then just click on it with the &RMB;, and select "
"<guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> or select an annotation using the &LMB; "
"and press the &Del; key."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti opombo, najprej izberite orodje za brskanje "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Brskaj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>), nato jo kliknite z &RMB; in izberite <guimenuitem> Izbriši</"
"guimenuitem> ali izberite opombo z &LMB; in pritisnite &Del; tipko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1219
#, no-c-format
msgid "When removing the annotation, its window will be closed if it is open."
msgstr "Pri odstranjevanju opombe bo njeno okno zaprto, če je odprto."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing annotations"
msgstr "Urejanje opomb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit an annotation, first select the Browse tool "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Browse</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>) then click on an annotation with the &RMB; and select "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem>. A dialog will appear with the general "
"annotation settings (like color and opacity, author, &etc;) and the settings "
"specific to that annotation type."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti opombo, najprej izberite orodje za brskanje "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Brskaj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>), nato kliknite opombo z &RMB; in izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>. Pojavilo se bo pogovorno okno s "
"splošnimi nastavitvami pripisov (kot so barva in motnost, avtor itd.) in "
"nastavitvami, značilnimi za to vrsto pripisov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Annotation Property Dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno lastnosti opombe</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Annotation Property Dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno lastnosti opombe</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move an annotation, hold down the &Ctrl; key, move the mouse pointer on "
"it and then start dragging with the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Če želite premakniti opombo, pridržite &Ctrl; tipko, premaknite kazalec "
"miške nanjo in nato začnite vleči z &LMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click with the &LMB; on an annotation, it gets selected. Resize "
"handles appear on the selection rectangle. When the cursor is moved over one "
"of the 8 resize handles on the corners or edges, the cursor shape changes to "
"indicate the resize mode. Click anywhere else on the annotation to move it. "
"Pressing &Esc; or clicking an area outside the annotation cancels a "
"selection."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete z &LMB; na opombi se izbere. Ročaji za spreminjanje velikosti se "
"prikažejo na izbirnem pravokotniku. Ko se kazalec premakne nad eno od 8 "
"ročic za spreminjanje velikosti na vogalih ali robovih, se oblika kazalca "
"spremeni, da prikaže način spreminjanja velikosti. Kliknite kjer koli drugje "
"pripis, da ga premaknete. S pritiskom &Esc; ali pa s klikom na območje zunaj "
"opombe prekličete izbor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resizing is only available for the Inline Note, Typewriter, Stamp and "
"Ellipse annotation types."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje velikosti je na voljo samo za anotacije: vrstične opombe, "
"pisalni stroj, žig in elipsa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some options may be disabled depending on the document's permissions (this "
"typically only affects some &PDF; documents)."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere možnosti so lahko onemogočene, odvisno od dovoljenj dokumenta (to "
"običajno vpliva le na nekatere dokumente &PDF;)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark Management"
msgstr "Upravljanje zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&okular; has a very flexible bookmark system. &okular; saves the position on "
"the page in bookmark and allows you to define more than one bookmark per "
"page."
msgstr ""
"&okular; ima zelo prilagodljiv sistem zaznamkov. &okular; shrani položaj na "
"strani v zaznamku in vam omogoča, da določite več kot en zaznamek na stran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To manage bookmarks in &okular; you can use <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> "
"view from <guilabel>Sidebar</guilabel>, <link linkend=\"menubookmarks"
"\">Bookmarks menu</link> or context menu of document view (click with &RMB; "
"to open it)."
msgstr ""
"Za upravljanje zaznamkov v programu &okular; lahko uporabite pogled "
"<guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel> v <guilabel>stranski vrstici</guilabel>, <link "
"linkend=\"menubookmarks\">meniju Zaznamkov</link> ali kontekstnem meniju "
"pogleda dokumenta (kliknite z &RMB;, da ga odprete )."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks view"
msgstr "Pogled zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> view, click on the "
"<guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> tab at the top of the <guilabel>Sidebar</"
"guilabel>. If the <guilabel>Sidebar</guilabel> is not shown, click the "
"<guibutton>Show Sidebar</guibutton> button on the toolbar or the menu item, "
"or the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>F7</keycap></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Sidebar</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item to make it visible."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti pogled <guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel>, kliknite zavihek "
"<guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel> na vrhu <guilabel>stranske vrstice</guilabel>. "
"Če <guilabel>stranska vrstica</guilabel> ni prikazana, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Pokaži stransko vrstico</guibutton> v orodni vrstici ali elementu "
"menija ali <menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži stransko vrstico</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> element menija, da bo viden."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Bookmark view context menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kontekstni meni pogleda zaznamkov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1281
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Bookmark view context menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kontekstni meni pogleda zaznamkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Show for all documents</guilabel> checkbox can be unchecked to "
"show only the bookmarks from the current document."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Pokaži za vse dokumente</guilabel> lahko "
"počistite, da prikažete samo zaznamke iz trenutnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filter bar at the top of <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> view can be used "
"to filter the content of bookmark list pane according to the text in the box."
msgstr ""
"Filtrirno vrstico na vrhu pogleda <guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel> lahko "
"uporabite za filtriranje vsebine podokna s seznamom zaznamkov glede na "
"besedilo v polju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list pane permits to view the bookmark list in a tree-like fashion: each "
"document in the list can be <quote>expanded</quote> or <quote>collapsed</"
"quote> by clicking on the <guiicon>&lt;</guiicon> or <guiicon>v</guiicon> "
"icon next to it."
msgstr ""
"Podokno s seznami omogoča ogled seznama zaznamkov v obliki drevesa: vsak "
"dokument na seznamu je mogoče <quote>razširiti</quote> ali <quote>strniti</"
"quote> s klikom na <guiicon>&lt;</guiicon> ali <guiicon>v</guiicon> zraven."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click menu of document item can be used to open document, rename its "
"item or remove it from the list. Remember that the removal of a document "
"item leads to the removal of all bookmarks in the corresponding document."
msgstr ""
"Z desnim klikom menija elementa dokumenta lahko odprete dokument, "
"preimenujete njegov element ali ga odstranite s seznama. Ne pozabite, da "
"odstranitev postavke dokumenta povzroči odstranitev vseh zaznamkov v "
"ustreznem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click menus of individual bookmark items allow you to go to the "
"bookmark, rename or remove it."
msgstr ""
"Meniji z desnim klikom posameznih elementov zaznamkov vam omogočajo, da "
"odprete zaznamek, ga preimenujete ali odstranite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Right-click menu of items in the table of contents can be used to create "
"bookmarks or go to the next or previous bookmark."
msgstr ""
"Meni elementov v kazalu z desnim klikom lahko uporabite za ustvarjanje "
"zaznamkov ali prehod na naslednji ali prejšnji zaznamek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1307
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Options"
msgstr "Možnosti ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Though &okular; may most often be started from the &kde; program menu, or a "
"desktop icon, it can also be opened at the command line prompt of a terminal "
"window. There are a few useful options that are available when doing this."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav se &okular; največkrat zažene iz &kde; programskega menija ali ikone "
"na namizju, ga lahko odprete tudi v ukazni vrstici okna terminala. Pri tem "
"je na voljo nekaj uporabnih možnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify a File"
msgstr "Določite datoteko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By specifying the path and name of a particular file the user can have "
"&okular; open that file immediately upon startup. This option might look "
"something like the following:"
msgstr ""
"Z določitvijo poti in imena določene datoteke lahko uporabnik &okular;ja "
"odpre to datoteko takoj po zagonu. Ta možnost je lahko videti nekako takole:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>okular</command> "
"<option><replaceable>/home/myhome/docs/mydoc.pdf</replaceable></option> </"
"userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>okular</command> "
"<option><replaceable>/home/myhome/docs/mydoc.pdf</replaceable></option> </"
"userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For &PDF; documents, the name can be given as <replaceable>document_name</"
"replaceable>#<replaceable>named_destination</replaceable> where "
"<replaceable>named_destination</replaceable> is a particular named "
"destination embedded in the document."
msgstr ""
"Za &PDF; dokumente, lahko ime podate kot <replaceable>ime_dokumenta</"
"replaceable>#<replaceable>ime_cilja</replaceable>, kjer je "
"<replaceable>ime_cilja</replaceable> določen imenovani cilj, vstavljen v "
"dokument."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Command Line Options"
msgstr "Druge možnosti ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1326
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following command line help options are available"
msgstr "Na voljo so naslednje možnosti pomoči v ukazni vrstici"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>okular</command> <option>-p --page <replaceable>number</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>okular</command> <option>-p --page <replaceable>število</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open a page with a given number in the document. Also available through "
"<userinput><command>okular</command> <option>-p <replaceable>number</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Odprite stran z dano številko v dokumentu. Na voljo tudi prek "
"<userinput><command>okular</command> <option>-p <replaceable>število</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1336
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>okular</command> <option>--presentation</option>"
msgstr "<command>okular</command> <option>--predstavitev</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start the document in presentation mode."
msgstr "Zaženite dokument v predstavitvenem načinu."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>okular</command> <option>--print</option>"
msgstr "<command>okular</command> <option>--print</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1343
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start with print dialog."
msgstr "Začni s pogovornim oknom za tiskanje."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1346
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>okular</command> <option>--print-and-exit</option>"
msgstr "<command>okular</command> <option>--print-and-exit</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start with print dialog and exit after printing."
msgstr "Začni s pogovornim oknom za tiskanje in zapusti po tiskanju."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>okular</command> <option>--unique</option>"
msgstr "<command>okular</command> <option>--unique</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unique instance control."
msgstr "Edinstveni nadzor primerkov."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1356
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>okular</command> <option>--noraise</option>"
msgstr "<command>okular</command> <option>--noraise</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows to prevent &okular; window raising after the start."
msgstr "Omogoča preprečevanje programu &okular; dvig oken po startu."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>okular</command> <option>--find <replaceable>string</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>okular</command> <option>--find <replaceable>niz</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tries to find and highlight a given string in the document. Only works if "
"just one document is given as an argument of the <userinput><command>okular</"
"command></userinput> command."
msgstr ""
"Poskuša najti in označiti dani niz v dokumentu. Deluje le, če je samo en "
"dokument podan kot argument ukaza <userinput><command>okular</command></"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>okular</command> <option>--editor-cmd <replaceable>string</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>okular</command> <option>--editor-cmd <replaceable>niz</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the external editor command. You cannot set the editor command in an "
"already running &okular; instance. Please note that <option>--unique</"
"option> is not supported when setting the editor command at the commandline."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi ukaz zunanjega urejevalnika. Ukaza urejevalnika ne morete nastaviti "
"v že delujoči instanci programa &okular;. Upoštevajte, da <option>--unique</"
"option> ni podprt pri nastavljanju ukaza urejevalnika v ukazni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fit window to page"
msgstr "Prilagodi okno strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Fit window to page feature resizes the window so that it is exactly the "
"same size as the page at the current zoom factor. If the page doesn't "
"completely fit on the screen, the window is enlarged so that the largest "
"possible part of the page is shown."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija Prilagodi okno strani spremeni velikost okna, tako da je popolnoma "
"enake velikosti kot stran pri trenutnem faktorju povečave. Če se stran ne "
"prilega v celoti na zaslon, se okno poveča, tako da je prikazan največji "
"možni del strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature can be accessed by using the keyboard shortcut <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Do te funkcije lahko dostopate z uporabo bližnjice na tipkovnici <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1386
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menubar"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1389
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open</action> a supported file or &okular; document archive. If "
"there is already an opened file it will be closed. For more information, see "
"the section about <link linkend=\"opening\">Opening Files</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpri</action> podprto datoteko ali &okular; arhiv dokumentov. Če že "
"obstaja odprta datoteka, bo zaprta. Za več informacij glejte razdelek o "
"<link linkend=\"opening\">odpiranju datotek</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1410
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Open Recent</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Odpri nedavno</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open</action> a file which was used previously from a submenu. If a "
"file is currently being displayed it will be closed. For more information, "
"see the section about <link linkend=\"opening\">Opening Files</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpri</action> datoteko, ki je bila prej uporabljena v podmeniju. Če "
"je datoteka trenutno prikazana, bo zaprta. Za več informacij glejte razdelek "
"o <link linkend=\"opening\">odpiranju datotek</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import PostScript as &PDF;...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uvozi PostScript kot &PDF;...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1446
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Open</action> a &PostScript; file and convert it to &PDF;."
msgstr "<action>Odpri</action> PostScript; datoteko in jo pretvorite v &PDF;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo close tab</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi "
"zapiranje zavihka</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Reopen</action> the last closed document. This action is active only "
"if you have closed some document in tab during the current session."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponovno odpri</action> nazadnje zaprt dokument. To dejanje je "
"aktivno samo, če ste med trenutno sejo zaprli kakšen dokument v zavihku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Containing Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri mapo, ki vsebuje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open</action> folder that contains the current document in your "
"favorite file manager. This action is especially useful for the case when "
"you have downloaded a &PDF; file from the internet that opens itself in "
"&okular;. The location of this file may not be clear or easy to find without "
"this feature."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpri</action> mapo, ki vsebuje trenutni dokument v vašem "
"priljubljenem upravitelju datotek. To dejanje je še posebej uporabno v "
"primeru, ko ste prenesli &PDF; datoteko iz interneta, ki se sama odpre v "
"&okular;ju. Lokacija te datoteke morda ne bo jasna ali jo bo enostavno najti "
"brez te funkcije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Saves</action> the document including all the changes (annotations, "
"form contents, &etc;), provided the document backend supports saving those "
"changes. If the backend does not support saving the changes, the user will "
"be given the option to either discard or to save them together with the "
"document in an &okular; document archive."
msgstr ""
"<action>Shrani</action> dokument, vključno z vsemi spremembami (opombe, "
"vsebina obrazca itd.), pod pogojem, da zaledje dokumenta podpira "
"shranjevanje teh sprememb. Če zaledje ne podpira shranjevanja sprememb, bo "
"uporabnik imel možnost, da jih zavrže ali shrani skupaj z dokumentom v "
"&okular;jev arhiv dokumentov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot..."
"</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Saves</action> the document under a new name including all the "
"changes (annotations, form contents, &etc;), provided the document backend "
"supports saving changes. If the backend does not support saving the changes, "
"the user will be given the option to either discard or to save them together "
"with the document in an &okular; document archive."
msgstr ""
"<action>Shrani</action> dokument pod novim imenom, vključno z vsemi "
"spremembami (opombe, vsebina obrazca itd.), pod pogojem, da zaledje "
"dokumenta podpira shranjevanje sprememb. Če zaledje ne podpira shranjevanja "
"sprememb, bo uporabnik imel možnost, da jih zavrže ali shrani skupaj z "
"dokumentom v &okular;jev arhiv dokumentov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that, due to the way this is implemented, even if there are no changes "
"to the file, the new file need not to be an exact bit-for-bit copy of the "
"original file (&eg; can have a different SHA-1 hash, &etc;)."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da zaradi načina izvajanja tega ni treba, da je nova datoteka "
"natančna bit-za-bitna kopija izvirne datoteke, tudi če datoteka ni "
"spremenjena (npr. lahko ima drugačen SHA-1 hash itd.)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Osveži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1527
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Reload</action> the currently open file."
msgstr "<action>Osveži</action> trenutno odprto datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Print</action> the currently displayed document. Please take into "
"account that &okular; has some specific options for printing &PDF; which are "
"available via pressing the <guibutton>Options >></guibutton> button then "
"choosing the <guilabel>&PDF; Options</guilabel>. Use these options to print "
"your annotations or configure rasterization mode if you have problems with "
"printing some symbols or need to change the scale mode."
msgstr ""
"<action>Natisni</action> trenutno prikazan dokument. Upoštevajte, da ima "
"&okular; nekaj posebnih možnosti za tiskanje &PDF; ki so na voljo tako, da "
"pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Možnosti >></guibutton> in nato izberete "
"<guilabel>&PDF; Možnosti</guilabel>. Uporabite te možnosti za tiskanje opomb "
"ali konfiguracijo načina rastriranja, če imate težave s tiskanjem nekaterih "
"simbolov ali morate spremeniti način merila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scale mode options are only available when you check the <guilabel>Force "
"rasterization</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti načina merila so na voljo le, če označite možnost <guilabel>Vsili "
"rastrizacijo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1553
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print Preview...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show a preview</action> of how the currently displayed document "
"would be printed with the default options."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pokaži predogled</action> tega, kako bi bil trenutno prikazan "
"dokument natisnjen s privzetimi možnostmi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Return</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Return</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Display some basic information</action> about the document, such as "
"title, author, creation date, and details about the fonts used. The "
"available information depends on the type of document."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaži nekaj osnovnih informacij</action> o dokumentu, kot so "
"naslov, avtor, datum nastanka in podrobnosti o uporabljenih pisavah. "
"Razpoložljive informacije so odvisne od vrste dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please pay attention on the information about substituting font in the "
"<guilabel>Fonts</guilabel> tab of the <guilabel>Properties</guilabel> "
"dialog. Many problems with font rendering can be solved by installing of the "
"substituted fonts."
msgstr ""
"Prosimo, bodite pozorni na informacije o zamenjavi pisave na zavihku "
"<guilabel>Pisave</guilabel> pogovornega okna <guilabel>Lastnosti</guilabel>. "
"Veliko težav z upodabljanjem pisav je mogoče rešiti z namestitvijo "
"nadomeščenih pisav."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1585
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Embedded Files...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vstavljene datoteke...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show the files embedded</action> in the document, if the document "
"has any. For more information, see the section about the <link linkend="
"\"embedded-files\">Embedded Files</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pokaži datoteke, vstavljene</action> v dokument, če jih ima "
"dokument. Za več informacij si oglejte razdelek o <link linkend=\"embedded-"
"files\">vstavljenih datotekah</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1599
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Export As</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izvozi kot</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item contains the export formats the current document can be exported "
"to. The first entry for all kind of documents is always <guimenuitem>Plain "
"Text...</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Ta element vsebuje izvozne formate, v katere je mogoče izvoziti trenutni "
"dokument. Prvi vnos za vse vrste dokumentov je vedno <guimenuitem>Navadno "
"besedilo...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second entry is <guimenuitem>Document Archive</guimenuitem>, which "
"allows you to save the document with your annotations into an &okular;-"
"specific archive format. Thus it is easily possible to share the original "
"document and your annotations with other &okular; users or work with them "
"collaboratively."
msgstr ""
"Drugi vnos je <guimenuitem>Arhiv dokumentov</guimenuitem>, ki vam omogoča, "
"da dokument s svojimi opombami shranite v arhivski format, specifičen za "
"&okular;. Tako je preprosto mogoče deliti izvirni dokument in vaše opombe z "
"drugimi uporabniki &okular;ja ali delati z njimi skupaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1613
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Share</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Deli</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1619
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item contains the services which can be used to share the current "
"document with other people or send it to your devices. The entries in this "
"sub-menu are controlled by the system. They depend on the current document "
"format and the installed KPurpose plugins."
msgstr ""
"Ta element vsebuje storitve, ki jih je mogoče uporabiti za skupno rabo "
"trenutnega dokumenta z drugimi ljudmi ali za pošiljanje v vaše naprave. "
"Vnose v tem podmeniju nadzira sistem. Odvisne so od trenutnega formata "
"dokumenta in nameščenih vtičnikov KPurpose."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Opusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1633
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Close</action> &okular;."
msgstr "<action>Zapri</action> &okular;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1640
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Undo</action> the last annotation editing command (creation and "
"removal of annotations, editing arbitrary annotation properties, relocating "
"annotations with &Ctrl;+drag, and editing the text contents of an "
"annotation)."
msgstr ""
"<action>Razveljavi</action> zadnji ukaz za urejanje pripisov (ustvarjanje in "
"odstranjevanje pripisov, urejanje poljubnih lastnosti pripisov, premeščanje "
"pripisov z &Ctrl;+vlečenjem in urejanje besedilne vsebine pripisov)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1665
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Redo</action> the last undo step when editing annotations."
msgstr "<action>Ponovi</action> zadnji korak razveljavitve pri urejanju opomb."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Copy</action> the currently selected text in <guibutton>Text "
"Selection</guibutton> mode to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"<action>Kopiraj</action> trenutno izbrano besedilo v načinu "
"<guibutton>Izbira besedila</guibutton> v odložišče."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1696
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Selects</action> all the text (if the document provides it). This "
"works only in <guibutton>Text Selection</guibutton> mode."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izbere</action> celotno besedilo (če ga dokument ponuja). To deluje "
"samo v načinu <guibutton>Izbira besedila</guibutton>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All Text on Current Page</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi vse besedilo na trenutni "
"strani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Selects</action> all the text (if the document provides it) of the "
"current page."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izbere</action> vse besedilo (če ga dokument ponuja) trenutne strani."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Najdi...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1727
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show the find bar on the bottom of the viewing area that allows you to "
"<action>search for a string in the document</action>."
msgstr ""
"Pokaži vrstico za iskanje na dnu območja za ogled, ki vam omogoča "
"<action>iskanje niza v dokumentu</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F3</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F3</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Najdi naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to <action>find the previous searched string again</action> in the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite <action>ponovno najti prejšnji iskani niz</action> v dokumentu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči prejšnje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Goes to the previous occurrence of the search string</action> in the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pomakne se na prejšnjo pojavitev iskalnega niza</action> v dokumentu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1763
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>P</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Presentation</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>P</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predstavitev</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Activates</action> the Presentation Mode. For more information, see "
"the section about <link linkend=\"presentationMode\">Presentation Mode</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Aktivira</action> način predstavitve. Za več informacij si oglejte "
"razdelek o <link linkend=\"presentationMode\">predstavitvenem načinu</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Full Screen Mode</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Celozaslonski "
"način</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Enables the full screen mode</action>. Note that full screen mode is "
"different from presentation mode insofar as the only peculiarity of full "
"screen mode is that it hides the window decorations, the menubar and the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogoči celozaslonski način</action>. Upoštevajte, da se "
"celozaslonski način razlikuje od predstavitvenega načina, saj je edina "
"posebnost celozaslonskega načina ta, da skrije okraske oken, menijsko "
"vrstico in orodno vrstico."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1795
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom In</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1802
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Increase the magnification</action> of the document view."
msgstr "<action>Povečajte povečavo</action> pogleda dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom Out</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pomanjšaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1815
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Decrease the magnification</action> of the document view."
msgstr "<action>Zmanjšajte povečavo</action> pogleda dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1820
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom to 100%</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj do 100 %</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1826
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Zoom the document image to the actual size</action> as prescribed by "
"the document parameters."
msgstr ""
"<action>Povečajte sliko dokumenta na dejansko velikost</action>, kot je "
"predpisano s parametri dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1831
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Fit Width</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilagodi širini</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Change the magnification</action> of the document view to a value "
"that makes the pages' width equal to the document view's width."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spremenite povečavo</action> pogleda dokumenta na vrednost, zaradi "
"katere je širina strani enaka širini pogleda dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1844
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Fit Page</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilagodi strani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1850
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Change the magnification</action> of the document view to a value "
"that makes at least one whole page visible."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spremenite povečavo</action> pogleda dokumenta na vrednost, zaradi "
"katere bo vidna vsaj ena cela stran."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1856
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Auto Fit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Samodejno prilagajanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Change the magnification</action> of the document view to a value "
"that, depending on the size relation between the page and the view area, "
"automatically either makes the pages' width equal to the document view's "
"width (like fit-width), the pages' height equal to the document view's "
"height (like fit-height), or the whole page visible (like fit-page)."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spremenite povečavo</action> pogleda dokumenta na vrednost, ki glede "
"na razmerje velikosti med stranjo in območjem pogleda samodejno bodisi "
"izenači širino strani s širino pogleda dokumenta (kot je širina "
"prileganja ), višina strani enaka višini pogleda dokumenta (kot fit-height) "
"ali vidna cela stran (kot fit-page)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1868
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Način pogleda</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1874
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu makes you choose the view mode for the pages. The possible "
"options are: <guimenuitem>Single Page</guimenuitem> (only one page per row), "
"<guimenuitem>Facing Pages</guimenuitem> (two pages per row, in a book "
"style), <guimenuitem>Facing Pages (Center First Page)</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Overview</guimenuitem> (the number of columns is the one "
"specified in the <link linkend=\"configure\">&okular; settings</link>)."
msgstr ""
"V tem podmeniju lahko izberete način pogleda za strani. Možne možnosti so: "
"<guimenuitem>Ena stran</guimenuitem> (samo ena stran na vrstico), "
"<guimenuitem>Obrnjene strani</guimenuitem> (dve strani na vrstico, v "
"knjižnem slogu), <guimenuitem>Obrnjene strani (na sredino prva stran)</"
"guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Pregled</guimenuitem> (število stolpcev je "
"tisto, ki je določeno v <link linkend=\"configure\">&okular; nastavitvah</"
"link>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1880
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, you can enable the <guimenuitem>Continuous</guimenuitem> mode. "
"In continuous mode, all pages of the document are shown, and you can "
"smoothly scroll through them. Otherwise, only one page (or one row of pages) "
"is shown at a time."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko omogočite način <guimenuitem>Neprekinjeno</guimenuitem>. V "
"neprekinjenem načinu so prikazane vse strani dokumenta in se lahko gladko "
"premikate po njih. V nasprotnem primeru je naenkrat prikazana samo ena stran "
"(ali ena vrstica strani)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1888
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Orientation</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Usmerjenost</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu allows you to <action>changes the orientation</action> of the "
"pages of the document."
msgstr ""
"Ta podmeni vam omogoča, da <action>spremenite orientacijo</action> strani "
"dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1899
#, no-c-format
msgid "The rotation is applied to the orientation of every page."
msgstr "Vrtenje se uporablja za orientacijo vsake strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select <guimenuitem>Original Orientation</guimenuitem> to restore "
"the orientation of the document, discarding all the rotations applied "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko <guimenuitem>Izvirna orientacija</guimenuitem>, da obnovite "
"orientacijo dokumenta in zavržete vse ročno narejene zasuke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1912
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Trim View</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Trim View</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1918
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu allows you to remove the white border of pages when viewing "
"pages (<guimenuitem>Trim Margins</guimenuitem> item) or trim viewport to "
"selection (<guimenuitem>Trim To Selection</guimenuitem> item)."
msgstr ""
"Ta podmeni vam omogoča, da med ogledovanjem strani odstranite belo obrobo "
"strani (element <guimenuitem>Obreži robove</guimenuitem>) ali obrežite vidno "
"polje na izbor (element <guimenuitem>Obreži na izbor</guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>trim to selection</quote> mode allows you to draw a selection "
"over the rendered page in order to define a visible bounding box to be "
"applied to <emphasis>all pages</emphasis> in the document. Selecting a small "
"trim bounding box enforces minimum dimensions size (20% as a percentage of "
"total page size)."
msgstr ""
"Način <quote>obreži na izbor</quote> vam omogoča, da narišete izbor čez "
"upodobljeno stran, da določite vidno omejevalno polje, ki bo uporabljeno za "
"<emphasis>vse strani</emphasis> v dokumentu. Izbira majhnega omejevalnega "
"polja za obrezovanje uveljavi najmanjšo velikost dimenzij (20 % kot odstotek "
"celotne velikosti strani)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>trim margins</quote> mode is persistent across &okular; restarts. "
"The <quote>trim to selection</quote> mode is forgotten across &okular; "
"restarts."
msgstr ""
"Način <quote>obrezanja robov</quote> je obstojen po ponovnih zagonih "
"programa. Način <quote>obreži na izbor</quote> je pozabljen po ponovnih "
"zagonih programa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you switch &okular; from <quote>trim margins</quote> mode to "
"<quote>trim to selection</quote> mode, the view jumps out of <quote>trim "
"margins</quote> mode for the bounding box selection interaction."
msgstr ""
"Ko preklopite &okular; iz načina <quote>obreži robove</quote> v način "
"<quote>obreži na izbor</quote>, pogled skoči iz načina <quote>obreži robov</"
"quote> za interakcijo izbire omejevalne škatle."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The trim mode can be deactivated by selecting the same menu item that "
"activates it once again."
msgstr ""
"Način obrezovanja lahko deaktivirate tako, da ponovno izberete isto točko "
"menija, ki ga aktivira."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1937
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show/Hide Forms</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži/skrij obrazce</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show or hides the display</action> of the form fields of the "
"document."
msgstr "<action>Prikaži ali skrij prikaz</action> polj obrazca v dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1948
#, no-c-format
msgid "This menu item is active only if the current document has form fields."
msgstr ""
"Ta postavka menija je aktivna le, če ima trenutni dokument polja obrazca."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1960
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Go Menu"
msgstr "Meni Go"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1964
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous Page</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prejšnja stran</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1970
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>View the previous page</action> of the document."
msgstr "<action>Oglejte si prejšnjo stran</action> dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1975
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Page</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naslednja stran</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1981
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>View the next page</action> of the document."
msgstr "<action>Oglejte si naslednjo stran</action> dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Home;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Beginning of the document</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Home;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Začetek dokumenta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1993
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Go to the beginning</action> of the document."
msgstr "<action>Pojdi na začetek</action> dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>End of the document</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konec dokumenta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2005
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Go to the end</action> of the document."
msgstr "<action>Pojdi na konec</action> dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Left;</keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Left;</keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2017
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Go back to the previous view</action> of the document."
msgstr "<action>Nazaj na prejšnji pogled</action> dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2022
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Right;</keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Right;</keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2029
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Move forward to the next view</action> of the document. This only "
"works if you have already moved back before."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pomik naprej na naslednji pogled</action> dokumenta. To deluje le, "
"če ste se že pomaknili nazaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Page...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na stran...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2041
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open a dialog which allows you to <action>go to any page</action> of the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Odprite pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča, da <action>odprete katero koli "
"stran</action> dokumenta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2048
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "Meni z zaznamki"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2052
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add/Remove Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj/odstrani zaznamek</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2059
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Add or remove a bookmark for the current position</action>."
msgstr "<action>Dodaj ali odstrani zaznamek za trenutni položaj</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2066
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename Bookmark</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preimenuj zaznamek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2072
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Rename a bookmark for the current position</action>."
msgstr "<action>Preimenuj zaznamek za trenutni položaj</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2079
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous Bookmark</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prejšnji zaznamek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2085
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Go to the previous bookmark</action>, or do nothing if there are no "
"bookmarks prior to the current one."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pojdi na prejšnji zaznamek</action> ali ne naredi ničesar, če pred "
"trenutnim zaznamkom ni nobenega zaznamka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2091
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Bookmark</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naslednji zaznamek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2097
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Go to the next bookmark</action>, or do nothing if there are no "
"bookmarks after the current one."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pojdi na naslednji zaznamek</action> ali ne naredi ničesar, če za "
"trenutnim zaznamkom ni nobenega zaznamka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>No Bookmarks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Brez zaznamkov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is an always disabled action that appears in this menu only if the "
"current document has no bookmarks. Otherwise a list of all bookmarks is "
"displayed here. Clicking on these bookmarks allows you to go directly to the "
"associated position."
msgstr ""
"To je vedno onemogočeno dejanje, ki se prikaže v tem meniju le, če trenutni "
"dokument nima zaznamkov. V nasprotnem primeru je tukaj prikazan seznam vseh "
"zaznamkov. S klikom na te zaznamke se lahko pomaknete neposredno na povezan "
"položaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2118
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Browse</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Brskaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse will have its normal behavior, &LMB; for dragging the document and "
"following links and &RMB; for adding bookmarks and fit to width."
msgstr ""
"Miška se bo normalno obnašala, &LMB; za vlečenje dokumenta in sledenje "
"povezavam ter &RMB; za dodajanje zaznamkov in prilagajanje širini."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Povečava</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse will work as a zoom tool. Clicking &LMB; and dragging will zoom "
"the view to the selected area, clicking &RMB; will bring the document back "
"to the previous zoom."
msgstr ""
"Miška bo delovala kot orodje za povečavo. S klikom na &LMB; in vlečenje bo "
"povečalo pogled na izbrano območje, kliknite &RMB; bo vrnil dokument na "
"prejšnjo povečavo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>3</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Area Selection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>3</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izbira območja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse will work as a rectangular region selection tool. In that mode "
"clicking &LMB; and dragging will draw a selection box and provide the option "
"of copying the selected content to the clipboard, speaking the selected "
"text, or transforming the selection region into an image and saving it to a "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Miška bo delovala kot orodje za izbiro pravokotne regije. V tem načinu s "
"klikom &LMB; in vlečenjem nariše izbirno polje in ponudi možnost kopiranja "
"izbrane vsebine v odložišče, izgovorjavo izbranega besedila ali "
"preoblikovanje izbirnega območja v sliko in shranjevanje v datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>4</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Text Selection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>4</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izbira besedila</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse will work as a text selection tool. In that mode clicking &LMB; "
"and dragging will give the option of selecting the text of the document. "
"Then, just click with the &RMB; to copy to the clipboard or speak the "
"current selection."
msgstr ""
"Miška bo delovala kot orodje za izbiro besedila. V tem načinu bo s klikom "
"&LMB; in vlečenjem dalo možnost izbire besedila dokumenta. Nato samo "
"kliknite z &RMB; da kopirate v odložišče ali izgovorite trenutni izbor."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Table Selection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izbor seznama</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draw a rectangle around the text for the table, then click with the &LMB; to "
"divide the text block into rows and columns. A &LMB; click on an existing "
"line removes it and merges the adjacent rows or columns. Finally, just click "
"with the &RMB; to copy the table to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Okoli besedila tabele narišite pravokotnik, nato kliknite z &LMB; za "
"razdelitev besedilnega bloka v vrstice in stolpce. &LMB; klik na obstoječo "
"vrstico jo odstrani in združi sosednje vrstice ali stolpce. Nazadnje samo "
"kliknite z &RMB; da kopirate tabelo v odložišče."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Magnifier</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lupa</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activates the magnifier mode for the mouse pointer. Press and hold the &LMB; "
"to activate magnifier widget, move the pointer for panning through the "
"document. The magnifier scales each pixel in the document into 10 pixels in "
"the magnifier widget."
msgstr ""
"Aktivira način lupe za kazalec miške. Pritisnite in držite &LMB; če želite "
"aktivirati gradnik lupe, premaknite kazalec za pomikanje po dokumentu. Lupa "
"poveča vsako slikovno piko v dokumentu v 10 slikovnih pik v gradniku lupe."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F6</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Annotations</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F6</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Opombe</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open the annotation toolbar</action>. The annotation toolbar allows "
"you to add annotations on the document you are reading. For more "
"information, please see the section about <link linkend=\"annotations"
"\">Annotations</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odprite orodno vrstico za opombe</action>. Orodna vrstica za opombe "
"vam omogoča dodajanje opomb dokumentu, ki ga berete. Za več informacij si "
"oglejte razdelek o <link linkend=\"annotations\">Pripombah</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2215
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Digitally Sign...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Digitalni podpis ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Starts the digital signature creation workflow</action>. Addition of "
"digital signatures is only supported for PDF files at this point. For more "
"information, please see the section about <link linkend="
"\"adding_digital_signatures\">Adding Digital Signatures</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zažene potek dela za ustvarjanje digitalnega podpisa</action>. "
"Dodajanje digitalnih podpisov je trenutno podprto samo za datoteke PDF. Za "
"več informacij si oglejte razdelek o <link linkend="
"\"adding_digital_signatures\">Dodajanju digitalnih podpisov</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Speak Whole Document</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izgovori celoten dokument</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Speak Current Page</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izgovori trenutno stran</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop Speaking</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nehaj govoriti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pause/Resume Speaking</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Začasno ustavi/nadaljuj govor</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These items allow you to speak the whole document or just the current page "
"and stop speaking using the system speech service. This service is provided "
"by a &Qt; library which wraps speech-dispatcher on &Linux;, and native "
"speech systems on other platforms. It is possible to choose the current "
"voice via &okular; <link linkend=\"configaccessibility\">Accessibility</"
"link> configuration page."
msgstr ""
"Ti elementi vam omogočajo, da izgovorite celoten dokument ali samo trenutno "
"stran in prekinete govor z uporabo sistemske govorne storitve. To storitev "
"zagotavlja &Qt; knjižnica, ki ovija govorni dispečer na &Linux;u in sisteme "
"maternega govora na drugih platformah. Možno je izbrati trenutni glas preko "
"programa &okular; Stran s konfiguracijo <link linkend=\"configaccessibility"
"\">Dostopnost</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Speak ...</guilabel> actions are enabled only if a speech "
"service is available in the system."
msgstr ""
"Dejanja <guilabel>Govori ...</guilabel> so omogočena samo, če je govorna "
"storitev na voljo v sistemu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2260
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami in pomočjo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu> menus described in the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html"
"\">Menu</ulink> chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals documentation &okular; has "
"these application specific menu entries:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg običajnega &kde; Menija sta <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in "
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> opisana v poglavju <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html\">Meni</ulink> v &kde; Dokumentaciji o osnovah &okular;ja ima te "
"menijske vnose za posamezne aplikacije:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F7</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Sidebar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F7</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži stransko vrstico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows or hides the Sidebar."
msgstr "Prikaže ali skrije stransko vrstico."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2279
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Page Bar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži vrstico strani</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle the page bar</action> at the bottom of document area on and "
"off to save vertical place in &okular; window. Note that the page numbers "
"will be shown on the default toolbar anyway."
msgstr ""
"<action>Vklopite in izklopite vrstico strani</action> na dnu območja "
"dokumenta, da shranite navpično mesto v &okular;jevem oknu. Upoštevajte, da "
"bodo številke strani vseeno prikazane v privzeti orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Backends...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj ozadja...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"configure-backends\">Backend Configuration</link> "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno <link linkend=\"configure-backends\">Konfiguracija ozadja</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &okular; Backends"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure &okular; backends by choosing <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Backends...</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice>. Currently, configuration options are provided for EPub, "
"&PostScript;, FictionBook, Txt, OpenDocument Text, and &PDF; backends only."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko &okular; ozadja tako, da izberete <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj ozadja...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Trenutno so konfiguracijske možnosti na voljo za "
"samo EPub, &PostScript;, FictionBook, Txt, OpenDocument Text in &PDF; "
"zaledja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The backends configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo ozadja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2320
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The backends configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo ozadja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using backend configuration pages for EPub, FictionBook, Mobipocket, "
"Markdown, TXT, and OpenDocument Text you can define the font to render "
"documents in the corresponding formats. The <guibutton>Choose...</guibutton> "
"button in these pages opens standard &kde; font configuration window. Please "
"refer to the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/fonts.html\">&kde; Fundamentals "
"documentation</ulink> for the details."
msgstr ""
"Z zalednimi konfiguracijskimi stranmi za EPub, FictionBook, Mobipocket, "
"Markdown, TXT in OpenDocument Text lahko določite pisavo za upodabljanje "
"dokumentov v ustreznih formatih. Gumb <guibutton>Izberi...</guibutton> na "
"teh straneh odpre standardno &kde; okno za konfiguracijo pisave. Oglejte si "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/fonts.html\">&kde; Dokumentacija o osnovah</"
"ulink> za podrobnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The description of Markdown, &PostScript; and &PDF; backends configuration "
"pages can be found below."
msgstr ""
"Opis aplikacije Markdown, &PostScript; in &PDF; konfiguracijske strani "
"ozadij najdete spodaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Markdown backend configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija zaledja Markdown"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure &okular; Markdown rendering backend based on <ulink url="
"\"https://www.pell.portland.or.us/~orc/Code/markdown/\">Discount</ulink> by "
"choosing <guilabel>Markdown</guilabel> from the list on the left part of the "
"configuration dialog. An additional configurable option is as follows."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko zaledje &okular; ki upodablja markdown na podlagi <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.pell.portland.or.us/~orc/Code/markdown/\">popusta</ulink> "
"z izbiro <guilabel>Markdown</guilabel> seznam na levem delu "
"konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna. Dodatna nastavljiva možnost je naslednja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable SmartyPants formatting"
msgstr "Omogoči formatiranje SmartyPants"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked this option allows &okular; to process <ulink url=\"https://"
"daringfireball.net/projects/smartypants/\">SmartyPants</ulink> formatting. "
"Such formatting can be troublesome in the technical texts because of "
"unwanted substitutions (&eg;, it replaces <literal>(C)</literal> with a "
"copyright symbol). This option is checked by default."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označena, ta možnost dovoljuje &okular; za obdelavo oblikovanja <ulink "
"url=\"https://daringfireball.net/projects/smartypants/\">SmartyPants</"
"ulink>. Takšno oblikovanje je lahko v tehničnih besedilih težavno zaradi "
"nezaželenih zamenjav (npr. zamenja <literal>(C)</literal> s simbolom "
"avtorskih pravic). Ta možnost je privzeto označena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2350
#, no-c-format
msgid "&PostScript; backend configuration"
msgstr "&PostScript; konfiguracija zaledja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure &okular; &PostScript; rendering backend based on <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.ghostscript.com/\">Ghostscript</ulink> by choosing "
"<guilabel>Ghostscript</guilabel> from the list on the left part of the "
"configuration dialog. The only configurable option is as follows."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko &okular; &PostScript; upodabljanje zaledja na podlagi "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.ghostscript.com/\">Ghostscripta</ulink> tako, da "
"izberete <guilabel>Ghostscript</guilabel> s seznama v levem delu "
"konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna. Edina nastavljiva možnost je naslednja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use platform fonts"
msgstr "Uporabite pisave platforme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option determines whether Ghostscript should be allowed to use platform "
"fonts, if unchecked only usage of fonts embedded in the document will be "
"allowed. This option is checked by default."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost določa, ali naj bo Ghostscriptu dovoljena uporaba pisav "
"platforme; če ni potrjena, bo dovoljena samo uporaba pisav, vdelanih v "
"dokument. Ta možnost je privzeto označena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2369
#, no-c-format
msgid "&PDF; backend configuration"
msgstr "&PDF; konfiguracija zaledja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure &okular; &PDF; rendering backend based on <ulink url="
"\"https://poppler.freedesktop.org/\">Poppler</ulink> by choosing "
"<guilabel>&PDF;</guilabel> from the list on the left part of the "
"configuration dialog. The only configurable option is as follows."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko &okular; upodabljanje &PDF; zaledja, ki temelji na "
"<ulink url=\"https://poppler.freedesktop.org/\">Poppler</ulink>, tako da na "
"seznamu v levem delu konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna izberete "
"<guilabel>&PDF;</guilabel>. Edina nastavljiva možnost je naslednja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enhance thin lines"
msgstr "Izboljšajte tanke črte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drawing lines in &okular; is implemented in two steps: generation of the "
"clipping path and filling this clipping path. When the line in the original "
"document is less than one pixel this two step implementation could cause "
"problems. For those lines, the clipping path is filled with the filling "
"color that depends on the thickness of the line part inside the clipping "
"area. If the part of the line inside the clipping area gets very small the "
"contrast between the shape and the background color can become too low for "
"the line to be recognizable. The grids of such lines then looks very "
"unpretty."
msgstr ""
"Risanje črt v &okular;ju se izvaja v dveh korakih: ustvarjanje izrezovalne "
"poti in polnjenje te izrezovalne poti. Če je vrstica v izvirnem dokumentu "
"manjša od ene slikovne pike, lahko ta dvostopenjska izvedba povzroči težave. "
"Za te črte je pot izrezovanja napolnjena z barvo polnila, ki je odvisna od "
"debeline dela črte znotraj območja izrezovanja. Če del črte znotraj območja "
"izrezovanja postane zelo majhen, lahko postane kontrast med obliko in barvo "
"ozadja prenizek, da bi bila črta prepoznavna. Mreže takšnih črt potem "
"izgledajo zelo neljubo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Thin line (red), its clipping path (dashed line) and pixel boundaries (black "
"solid lines)"
msgstr ""
"Tanka črta (rdeča), njena izrezovalna pot (črtkana črta) in meje slikovnih "
"pik (polne črne črte)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2412
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thin line shown at a low contrast"
msgstr "Tanka črta, prikazana z nizkim kontrastom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2417
#, no-c-format
msgid "To enhance the look of the thin lines &okular; implements two options."
msgstr "Za izboljšanje videza tankih linij &okular; izvaja dve možnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first option is <guimenuitem>Solid</guimenuitem>. With this option "
"&okular; adjusts clipping path and line position so that clipping path and "
"line are on the same pixel boundary, &ie; &okular; enlarges the thin lines "
"to one pixel on the output device. This mode is similar to the "
"<guilabel>Enhance thin lines</guilabel> in <trademark class=\"registered"
"\">Adobe</trademark> <trademark class=\"registered\">Reader</trademark>. If "
"this option is chosen, the thin lines are always enlarged."
msgstr ""
"Prva možnost je <guimenuitem >Trdna</guimenuitem >. S to možnostjo &okular; "
"prilagodi položaj izrezovalne poti in črte, tako da sta izrezovalna pot in "
"črta na isti meji pikslov, tj. &okular; poveča tanke črte na eno slikovno "
"piko na izhodni napravi. Ta način je podoben <guilabel>Izboljšajte tanke "
"črte</guilabel> v <trademark class=\"registered\">Adobe</trademark> "
"<trademark class=\"registered\">Reader</trademark>. Če izberete to možnost, "
"so tanke črte vedno povečane."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Thin line with <guimenuitem>Solid</guimenuitem> enhancement</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Tanka linija z <guimenuitem>Trdno</guimenuitem> izboljšavo </phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>Thin line with <guimenuitem>Solid</guimenuitem> enhancement</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Tanka linija z <guimenuitem>Trdno</guimenuitem> izboljšavo </para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second option is <guimenuitem>Shape</guimenuitem>. With this option the "
"clipping path and line are adjusted to pixel boundary as well, but the line "
"intensity is corrected according to its width."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je <guimenuitem >Oblika</guimenuitem >. S to možnostjo se "
"izrezovalna pot in črta prav tako prilagodita meji slikovnih pik, vendar se "
"intenzivnost črte popravi glede na njeno širino."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Thin line with <guimenuitem>Shape</guimenuitem> enhancement</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Tanka črta z izboljšavo <guimenuitem>oblike</guimenuitem></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>Thin line with <guimenuitem>Shape</guimenuitem> enhancement</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Tanka linija z izboljšavo <guimenuitem>oblike</guimenuitem></para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The thin lines are not enhanced by default (option <guimenuitem>No</"
"guimenuitem>)."
msgstr ""
"Tanke črte privzeto niso izboljšane (možnost <guimenuitem>Ne</guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2465
#, no-c-format
msgid "&PDF; Digital Signature Certificates"
msgstr "&PDF; Potrdila za digitalni podpis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section allows you to set a custom Certificate Database to use when "
"adding Digital Signatures to &PDF; files."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vam omogoča, da nastavite zbirko podatkov potrdil po meri za "
"uporabo pri dodajanju digitalnih podpisov v &PDF; datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It also lists the certificates available in the current Certificate Database "
"(if any)."
msgstr ""
"Navaja tudi seznam potrdil, ki so na voljo v trenutni zbirki podatkov "
"potrdil (če obstajajo)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Configuring &okular;</title>"
msgstr "<title>Konfiguracija &okular;ja</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2479
#, no-c-format
msgid "General configuration"
msgstr "Splošna konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure &okular; by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &okular;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The "
"configuration dialog is split into six sections. This chapter describes the "
"available options in detail."
msgstr ""
"&okular; lahko konfigurirate, tako da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&okular;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno je "
"razdeljeno na šest razdelkov. V tem poglavju so podrobno opisane "
"razpoložljive možnosti."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2488
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"configgeneral\">General</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"configgeneral\">Splošno</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"configaccessibility\">Accessibility</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"configaccessibility\">Dostopnost</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2494
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"configperformance\">Performance</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"configperformance\">Zmogljivost</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2497
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"configpresentation\">Presentation</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"configpresentation\">Predstavitev</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2500
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"configannotations\">Annotations</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"configannotations\">Opombe</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2503
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"configeditor\">Editor</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"configeditor\">Urejevalnik</link>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2507
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2513
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the currently installed backends, the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Backends...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item could be enabled. This particular "
"configuration dialog holds the configurations of the backends that can "
"actually be configured."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od trenutno nameščenih ozadij je lahko omogočen menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"zaledja...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To posebno konfiguracijsko pogovorno "
"okno vsebuje konfiguracije zaledij, ki jih je dejansko mogoče konfigurirati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2525
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošno</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2528
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use smooth scrolling"
msgstr "Uporabite gladko drsenje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to display animated transitions when scrolling using the mouse wheel "
"and keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se prikažejo animirani prehodi med pomikanjem s koleščkom miške in "
"tipkovnico."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2534
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show scrollbars"
msgstr "Pokaži drsne trakove"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whether to show scrollbars for the document view."
msgstr "Ali naj se prikažejo drsni trakovi za pogled dokumenta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2540
#, no-c-format
msgid "Link the thumbnails with the page"
msgstr "Povežite sličice s stranjo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether the thumbnails view should always display the current page or not."
msgstr "Ali naj pogled sličic vedno prikazuje trenutno stran ali ne."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show hints and info messages"
msgstr "Pokaži namige in informativna sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whether to show some informative messages on startup, file load, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Ali naj prikaže nekatera informativna sporočila ob zagonu, nalaganju "
"datoteke &etc;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2554
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notify about embedded files, forms, or signatures"
msgstr "Obvestite o vdelanih datotekah, obrazcih ali podpisih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to show informative panels about embedded files, forms or signatures "
"&etc;"
msgstr ""
"Ali želite prikazati informativne plošče o vdelanih datotekah, obrazcih ali "
"podpisih &etc;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display document title in titlebar if available"
msgstr "Prikaži naslov dokumenta v naslovni vrstici, če je na voljo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to show the current document title in the titlebar of &okular; "
"window. If no metadata for title found in the document or this item is "
"unchecked &okular; shows filename of the document."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se naslov trenutnega dokumenta prikaže v naslovni vrstici okna "
"&okular;. Če v dokumentu ni najdenih metapodatkov za naslov ali ta element "
"ni označen, &okular; prikaže ime datoteke dokumenta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2569
#, no-c-format
msgid "When not displaying document title"
msgstr "Ko ni prikazan naslov dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose any of two options, <guilabel>Display file name only</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Display full file path</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko eno od dveh možnosti, <guilabel>Prikaži samo ime datoteke</"
"guilabel> ali <guilabel>Prikaži celotno pot do datoteke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2576
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use custom background color"
msgstr "Uporabite barvo ozadja po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/colors.html\">choosing the document "
"background color</ulink> (the color around the displayed page). By default, "
"the &Qt; toolkit color is used when this option is unchecked."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/colors.html\">izbiro barve ozadja "
"dokumenta</ulink> (barva okoli prikazane strani). Privzeto je &Qt; barva "
"kompleta orodij se uporablja, ko ta možnost ni potrjena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open new files in tabs"
msgstr "Odprite nove datoteke v zavihkih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to open new documents in tabs. The tabs are disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Ali odpreti nove dokumente v zavihkih. Zavihki so privzeto onemogočeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default shortcuts to switch between tabs are <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>.</"
"keycap></keycombo> (<guilabel>Next tab</guilabel>) and <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo> (<guilabel>Previous tab</guilabel>)."
msgstr ""
"Privzete bližnjice za preklapljanje med zavihki so <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>."
"</keycap></keycombo> (<guilabel>Naslednji zavihek</guilabel>) in "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>,</keycap> </keycombo> (<guilabel>Prejšnji zavihek</"
"guilabel>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to existing tab if file is already open"
msgstr "Preklopite na obstoječi zavihek, če je datoteka že odprta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether &okular; should switch to a tab if the file is already open instead "
"of opening a new tab. This option is enabled by default. Can be toggled only "
"if <guilabel>Open new files in tabs</guilabel> is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ali bi &okular; moral preklopiti na zavihek, če je datoteka že odprta, "
"namesto da odpre nov zavihek. Ta možnost je privzeto omogočena. Lahko se "
"preklaplja le, če je omogočeno <guilabel>Odpri nove datoteke v zavihkih</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2598
#, no-c-format
msgid "Obey DRM limitations"
msgstr "Upoštevajte omejitve DRM"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether &okular; should obey <firstterm>DRM</firstterm> (Digital Rights "
"Management) restrictions. DRM limitations are used to make it impossible to "
"perform certain actions with &PDF; documents, such as copying content to the "
"clipboard. Note that in some configurations of &okular;, this option is not "
"available."
msgstr ""
"Ali mora &okular; upoštevati omejitve <firstterm>DRM</firstterm> "
"(upravljanje digitalnih pravic). Omejitve DRM se uporabljajo za onemogočanje "
"nekaterih dejanj z &PDF; dokumentov, kot je kopiranje vsebine v odložišče. "
"Upoštevajte, da v nekaterih konfiguracijah programa &okular; ta možnost ni "
"na voljo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reload document on file change"
msgstr "Ponovno naloži dokument ob spremembi datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether opened files should be automatically checked for changes and "
"updated, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se odprte datoteke samodejno preverijo glede sprememb in po potrebi "
"posodobijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2615
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show backend selection dialog"
msgstr "Pokaži pogovorno okno za izbiro zaledja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether &okular; should ask the user which backend to use in case of more "
"than one backend able to open the current file. If unchecked, &okular; will "
"use the backend with the highest priority."
msgstr ""
"Ali mora &okular; vprašati uporabnika, katero zaledje naj uporabi, če lahko "
"trenutno datoteko odpre več kot eno zaledje. Če ni označeno, bo &okular; "
"uporabil zaledje z najvišjo prioriteto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right to left reading direction"
msgstr "Smer branja od desne proti levi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to use right to left reading direction by default for the opened "
"files. Can be useful for <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Right-to-"
"left\">some writing systems</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se za odprte datoteke privzeto uporabi smer branja od desne proti "
"levi. Lahko je uporabno za <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Right-"
"to-left\">nekatere pisne sisteme</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2631
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open in continuous mode by default"
msgstr "Privzeto odprto v neprekinjenem načinu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to use the continuous mode by default. In continuous mode, all pages "
"of the document are shown, and you can smoothly scroll through them. "
"Otherwise, only one page (or one row of pages) is shown at a time."
msgstr ""
"Ali želite privzeto uporabiti neprekinjeni način. V neprekinjenem načinu so "
"prikazane vse strani dokumenta in se lahko gladko premikate po njih. V "
"nasprotnem primeru je naenkrat prikazana samo ena stran (ali ena vrstica "
"strani)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2639
#, no-c-format
msgid "When using Browse Tool, wrap cursor at screen edges"
msgstr "Ko uporabljate orodje za brskanje, zavijte kazalec na robove zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows endless scrolling around the entire document with the <link linkend="
"\"menutools\">Browse Tool</link>. If enabled, the mouse cursor will wrap to "
"the opposite end of the screen when it touches the borders while dragging "
"the document. This feature is only supported on X11."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča neskončno pomikanje po celotnem dokumentu z <link linkend=\"menutools"
"\">orodjem za brskanje</link>. Če je omogočeno, se kazalec miške zavije na "
"nasprotni konec zaslona, ko se med vlečenjem dokumenta dotakne robov. Ta "
"funkcija je podprta samo na X11."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2647
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview columns"
msgstr "Pregled nad stolpci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option represents the number of columns to use in the overview mode."
msgstr "Ta možnost predstavlja število stolpcev za uporabo v načinu pregleda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2655
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page Up/Down overlap"
msgstr "Prekrivanje strani gor/dol"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can define the percentage of the current viewing area that should "
"be visible after pressing &PgUp;/&PgDn; keys."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko določite odstotek trenutnega območja gledanja, ki naj bo viden "
"po pritisku &PgUp;/&PgDn; tipk."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2663
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Zoom"
msgstr "Privzeta povečava"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option specifies the default zoom mode for files which were never "
"opened before. For those files which were opened before, the previous zoom "
"mode is applied."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost določa privzeti način povečave za datoteko, ki še nikoli ni bila "
"odprta. Za datoteke, ki so bile odprte že prej, se uporabi prejšnji način "
"povečave."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2675
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Accessibility</title>"
msgstr "<title>Dostopnost</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2678
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw border around links"
msgstr "Narišite obrobo okoli povezav"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whether to draw a border around links."
msgstr "Ali naj nariše obrobo okoli povezav."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2684
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change colors"
msgstr "Spremeni barve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2686
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Enables</action> the color changing options."
msgstr "<action>Omogoči</action> možnosti spreminjanja barv."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color mode"
msgstr "Barvni način"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2692
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Defines</action> the color changing mode."
msgstr "<action>Določi</action> način spreminjanja barve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2695
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invert Colors"
msgstr "Obrni barve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Inverts</action> colors on the view, &ie; black objects will be "
"shown white."
msgstr ""
"<action>Obrne</action> barve na pogledu, tj. črni predmeti bodo prikazani "
"beli."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2701
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change Paper Color"
msgstr "Spremeni barvo papirja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Changes</action> the paper's color, &ie; the document's background."
msgstr "<action>Spremeni</action> barvo papirja, tj. ozadje dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2704
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The color can be selected using the <guilabel>Paper color</guilabel> swatch "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Barvo lahko izberete s spodnjim vzorcem <guilabel>Barva papirja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change Dark &amp; Light Colors"
msgstr "Spremeni temno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Changes</action> the dark and light color to your preference, that "
"means black will not be rendered as black but as the selected dark color and "
"white will not be rendered as white but as the selected light color."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spremeni</action> temno in svetlo barvo po vaših željah, kar pomeni, "
"da črna ne bo upodobljena kot črna, temveč kot izbrana temna barva, bela pa "
"ne bo upodobljena kot bela, ampak kot izbrana svetla barva."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Convert to Black &amp; White"
msgstr "Pretvori v črno-belo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Converts</action> the document to black and white. You can set the "
"threshold and the contrast. Setting the threshold to a higher value by "
"moving it to the right will result in lighter grays used."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pretvori</action> dokument v črno-belega. Nastavite lahko prag in "
"kontrast. Če prag nastavite na višjo vrednost s premikanjem v desno, bodo "
"uporabljene svetlejše sive barve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2725
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invert Lightness"
msgstr "Obrni svetlost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2727
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Inverts</action> lightness of all colors. Light and dark colors will "
"be swapped, but hue and saturation will not be affected. The Contrast in "
"images will usually be worse than in <guilabel>Invert Luma (sRGB Linear)</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Obrne</action> svetlost vseh barv. Svetle in temne barve bodo "
"zamenjane, vendar to ne bo vplivalo na odtenek in nasičenost. Kontrast v "
"slikah bo običajno slabši kot pri <guilabel>Obrni svetlost (linearno sRGB)</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2733
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invert Luma (sRGB Linear)"
msgstr "Obrni svetlost (linearno sRGB)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2735
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Inverts</action> luma of all colors. Light and dark will be swapped, "
"but hue and saturation will not be affected. The Contrast in images is "
"preserved better than in <guilabel>Invert Lightness</guilabel>, but graphics "
"and colorful text markup usually look worse. Uses sRGB luma coefficients, "
"but no gamma correction."
msgstr ""
"<action>Obrne</action> svetlost vseh barv. Svetlo in temno bosta zamenjana, "
"vendar to ne bo vplivalo na odtenek in nasičenost. Kontrast v slikah je "
"ohranjen bolje kot pri privzeti <guilabel>Obrni svetlost</guilabel>, vendar "
"so grafike in pisane oznake besedila običajno videti slabše. Uporablja "
"koeficiente svetilnosti sRGB, vendar brez korekcije gama."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invert Luma (Symmetric)"
msgstr "Obrni svetlost (simetrično)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Inverts</action> luma of all colors, using symmetric luma "
"coefficients. Light and dark will be swapped, but hue and saturation will "
"not be affected. Very similar to <guilabel>Invert Lightness</guilabel>, but "
"the contrast is in some cases better."
msgstr ""
"<action>Obrne</action> svetlost vseh barv z uporabo simetričnih koeficientov "
"svetlosti. Svetlo in temno bosta zamenjana, vendar to ne bo vplivalo na "
"odtenek in nasičenost. Zelo podobno kot <guilabel>Obrni svetlost</guilabel>, "
"vendar je kontrast v nekaterih primerih boljši."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2752
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shift Hue Positive"
msgstr "Premakni odtenek v pozitivno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Shifts</action> hue of all colors by 120 degrees. Can mitigate some "
"contrast problems in colorful graphics."
msgstr ""
"<action>Premakne</action> odtenek vseh barv za 120 stopinj. Lahko ublaži "
"nekatere težave s kontrastom pri barviti grafiki."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2759
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shift Hue Negative"
msgstr "Premakni odtenek v negativno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Shifts</action> hue of all colors by 240 degrees. Can mitigate some "
"contrast problems in colorful graphics."
msgstr ""
"<action>Premakne</action> odtenek vseh barv za 240 stopinj. Lahko ublaži "
"nekatere težave s kontrastom pri barviti grafiki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure keyboard shortcuts and toolbar actions for the color modes "
"using the corresponding menu items in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu "
"of the &okular; main window."
msgstr ""
"Bližnjice na tipkovnici in dejanja orodne vrstice za barvne načine lahko "
"konfigurirate z uporabo ustreznih elementov menija v meniju "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> v &okular;jevem glavnem oknu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2770
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text-to-speech engine"
msgstr "Mehanizem za pretvorbo besedila v govor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2772
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Allows you to choose</action> the text-to-speech (<abbrev>TTS</"
"abbrev>) engine to be used by &okular;. The default is <application>speechd</"
"application> <abbrev>TTS</abbrev>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogoča vam, da izberete</action> mehanizem za pretvorbo besedila v "
"govor (<abbrev>TTS</abbrev>), ki ga bo uporabljal &okular;. Privzeto je "
"<application>speechd</application> <abbrev>TTS</abbrev>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2777
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text-to-speech voice"
msgstr "Glas za pretvorbo besedila v govor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Allows you to choose</action> a voice for the text-to-speech engine "
"to be used by &okular;. You can use all languages and voices depending on "
"the available synthesizers on your platform. On &Linux;, speech-dispatcher "
"is used by default to determine available voices."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogoča vam, da izberete</action> glas za mehanizem za pretvorbo "
"besedila v govor, ki ga bo uporabljal &okular;. Uporabite lahko vse jezike "
"in glasove, odvisno od razpoložljivih sintetizatorjev na vaši platformi. V "
"&Linux;u se govorni dispečer privzeto uporablja za določanje razpoložljivih "
"glasov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2787
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Performance</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zmogljivost</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2790
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable transparency effects"
msgstr "Omogoči učinke prosojnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draw selections and other special graphics using transparency effects. "
"Disable the option to draw them using outline or opaque fill styles and "
"increase speed on selections."
msgstr ""
"Narišite izbore in druge posebne grafike z učinki prosojnosti. Onemogočite "
"možnost, da jih narišete z orisi ali neprozornimi slogi polnila in povečajte "
"hitrost izbir."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2798
#, no-c-format
msgid "Memory usage"
msgstr "Poraba pomnilnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&okular; can achieve best performance by tuning the memory usage, based on "
"your system and your tastes. The more memory you let it to use, the faster "
"the program will behave. The Default profile is good for every system, but "
"you can prevent &okular; from using more memory than necessary by selecting "
"the Low profile, or let it get the most out of your system using Aggressive. "
"Use Greedy profile to preload all pages without risk of system memory "
"overfull (only 50% of total memory or free memory will be used)."
msgstr ""
"&okular; lahko doseže najboljšo zmogljivost z nastavitvijo porabe pomnilnika "
"glede na vaš sistem in vaš okus. Več pomnilnika kot mu dovolite, hitreje se "
"bo program obnašal. Privzeti profil je dober za vsak sistem, vendar lahko "
"preprečite &okular;ju uporabo več pomnilnika, kot je potrebno, tako da "
"izberete nizek profil, ali pa pustite, da kar najbolje izkoristi vaš sistem "
"z uporabo agresivnega. Uporabite profil Greedy za vnaprejšnje nalaganje vseh "
"strani brez nevarnosti, da bo sistemski pomnilnik prepoln (uporabljenih bo "
"le 50 % celotnega pomnilnika ali prostega pomnilnika)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2808
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rendering options"
msgstr "Možnosti izvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using this group of options you can improve text and image rendering in "
"&okular;. The result depends on the device to display the document. "
"<guilabel>Enable Text Antialias</guilabel> and <guilabel>Enable Graphics "
"Antialias</guilabel> items can be used to switch on and off <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spatial_anti-aliasing\">spatial anti-"
"aliasing</ulink> of text and images in document, correspondingly. "
"<guilabel>Enable Text Hinting</guilabel> item is meant to be a switcher for "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Font_hinting\">font hinting</"
"ulink>. Antialiasing and hinting change how the documents are displayed, you "
"may want to tweak them to your preference."
msgstr ""
"S to skupino možnosti lahko izboljšate upodabljanje besedila in slik v "
"&okular;ju. Rezultat je odvisen od naprave za prikaz dokumenta. Elementa "
"<guilabel>Omogoči prevleko besedila</guilabel> in <guilabel>Omogoči prevleko "
"grafike</guilabel> lahko uporabite za vklop in izklop <ulink url=\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spatial_anti-aliasing\">prostorsko izravnavanje</"
"ulink> besedila in slik v dokumentu, ustrezno. Element <guilabel>Omogoči "
"namigovanje besedila</guilabel> je mišljen kot preklopnik za <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Font_hinting\">namigovanje pisave</ulink>. "
"Antialiasing in namigi spremenijo način prikaza dokumentov, morda jih boste "
"želeli prilagoditi svojim željam."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2819
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Presentation</title>"
msgstr "<title>Predstavitev</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2822
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advance every"
msgstr "Vsak vnaprej"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2824
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables automatic advancing of pages given a time period."
msgstr "Omogoča samodejno premikanje po straneh glede na časovno obdobje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2828
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loop after last page"
msgstr "Ponovi po zadnji strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When navigating on presentation mode and going past the last page the first "
"page will appear."
msgstr ""
"Pri navigaciji v predstavitvenem načinu in prehodu mimo zadnje strani se "
"prikaže prva stran."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2834
#, no-c-format
msgid "Touch navigation"
msgstr "Navigacija na dotik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to fine-tune touchscreen navigation with tapping in the "
"presentation using the following three possible values:"
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam natančno nastavitev navigacije po zaslonu na dotik s dotikom v "
"predstavitvi z uporabo naslednjih treh možnih vrednosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Tap left/right side to go back/forward</guilabel>: Tapping on the "
"left (right) half of the screen makes the presentation go to the previous "
"(next) slide."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dotaknite se leve/desne strani, da se pomaknete nazaj/naprej</"
"guilabel>: Če se dotaknete leve (desne) polovice zaslona, se predstavitev "
"premakne na prejšnji (naslednji) diapozitiv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Tap anywhere to go forward</guilabel> (default): Tapping on the "
"screen makes the presentation go to the next slide, no matter where the "
"screen is being tapped."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Tapnite kjer koli, da greste naprej</guilabel> (privzeto): Če se "
"dotaknete zaslona, se predstavitev premakne na naslednji diapozitiv, ne "
"glede na to, kje se dotaknete zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2845
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Disabled</guilabel>: Screen tapping does not do anything."
msgstr "<guilabel>Onemogočeno</guilabel>: tapkanje zaslona ne naredi ničesar."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2851
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background color"
msgstr "Barva ozadja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The color that will fill the part of the screen not covered by the page when "
"on presentation mode."
msgstr ""
"Barva, ki bo v predstavitvenem načinu zapolnila del zaslona, ki ga stran ne "
"pokriva."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2857
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse cursor"
msgstr "Kazalec miške"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether the mouse should be always hidden, always shown or hidden after a "
"small time of inactivity."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj bo miška vedno skrita, vedno prikazana ali skrita po kratkem času "
"nedejavnosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2863
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show progress indicator"
msgstr "Pokaži indikator napredka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2865
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to show a progress circle that shows the current page and the total "
"number of pages on the upper right corner of the presentation screen every "
"time you change the page."
msgstr ""
"Ali želite prikazati krog napredka, ki prikazuje trenutno stran in skupno "
"število strani v zgornjem desnem kotu predstavitvenega zaslona vsakič, ko "
"spremenite stran."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2870
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show summary page"
msgstr "Pokaži stran s povzetkom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to show a summary page at the beginning of the presentation with the "
"title, author and number of pages of the document."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se na začetku predstavitve prikaže stran s povzetkom z naslovom, "
"avtorjem in številom strani dokumenta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2876
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable transitions"
msgstr "Omogoči prehode"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this check box to enable or disable transition effects between pages."
msgstr ""
"S tem potrditvenim poljem omogočite ali onemogočite učinke prehoda med "
"stranmi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2882
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default transition"
msgstr "Privzeti prehod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The transition effect between page and page if the document does not specify "
"one. Set this to <guilabel>Random Transition</guilabel> to make &okular; "
"randomly choose one of the available effects."
msgstr ""
"Učinek prehoda med stranmi, če ga dokument ne določa. To nastavite na "
"<guilabel>Naključni prehod</guilabel>, da bo &okular; naključno izberal "
"enega od razpoložljivih učinkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2889
#, no-c-format
msgid "Placement"
msgstr "Postavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this section you can select the <guilabel>Screen</guilabel> used to "
"display the presentation."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku lahko izberete <guilabel>Zaslon</guilabel> za prikaz "
"predstavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2892
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Current Screen</guilabel> is same screen of the &okular; window "
"that starts the presentation mode."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Trenutni zaslon</guilabel> je enak zaslonu &okular;ja, ki zažene "
"predstavitveni način."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default Screen</guilabel> is the screen marked as default in the "
"xinerama configuration."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeti zaslon</guilabel> je zaslon, ki je v konfiguraciji "
"xinerama označen kot privzeti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Screen 0</guilabel>, <guilabel>Screen 1</guilabel> &etc; are the "
"available screens."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zaslon 0</guilabel>, <guilabel>Zaslon 1</guilabel> itd. so "
"razpoložljivi zasloni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2898
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drawing Tool Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija orodja za risanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Manage the colors of the pencil used when drawing on the pages during the "
"presentation mode."
msgstr ""
"Upravljajte barve svinčnika, ki se uporablja pri risanju po straneh v "
"predstavitvenem načinu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The Annotations page of the configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Stran z opombami v konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2914
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Annotations page of the configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Stran z opombami v konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2920
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotation toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica za opombe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows switching between <guimenuitem>Full Annotation Toolbar</guimenuitem> "
"(<link linkend=\"annotations-add\">default toolbar</link> in the top section "
"of the &okular; window) and <guimenuitem>Quick Annotation Toolbar</"
"guimenuitem> (sliding toolbar with your favorite tools at the right part of "
"the document pane)."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča preklapljanje med <guimenuitem>Orodno vrstico za polne opombe</"
"guimenuitem> (<link linkend=\"annotations-add\">privzeta orodna vrstica</"
"link> v zgornjem delu okna &okular;ja) in <guimenuitem>Orodno vrstico za "
"hitro opombo</guimenuitem > (drsna orodna vrstica z vašimi najljubšimi "
"orodji na desnem delu podokna dokumenta)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Author"
msgstr "Avtor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The author of the contents added on a document. Default is the name from the "
"<guilabel>Password &amp; User Account</guilabel> page of the "
"&systemsettings; module <guilabel>Account Details</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Avtor vsebine, dodane v dokument. Privzeto je ime iz <guilabel>Geslo &amp; "
"Uporabniški račun</guilabel> strani &systemsettings; v modulu "
"<guilabel>Podrobnosti o računu</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2933
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotation tools"
msgstr "Orodja za opombe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This pane is used to configure your <link linkend=\"annotations-add"
"\">annotation toolbar</link>."
msgstr ""
"To podokno se uporablja za konfiguracijo vaše <link linkend=\"annotations-add"
"\">orodne vrstice za opombe</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2938
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are five buttons (<guibutton>Add</guibutton>, <guibutton>Edit</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>Remove</guibutton>, <guibutton>Move Up</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>Move Down</guibutton>) and a list box (which lists the contents "
"of the current annotation toolbar) which are used to configure the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja pet gumbov (<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>, <guibutton>Uredi</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton>, <guibutton>Premakni gor</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>Premakni dol</guibutton >) in polje s seznamom (v "
"katerem je navedena vsebina trenutne orodne vrstice z opombami), ki se "
"uporabljata za konfiguracijo orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to add some tool button on the toolbar click on the "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> button. You can choose the <guilabel>Name</"
"guilabel>, the <guilabel>Type</guilabel> and the <guilabel>Appearance</"
"guilabel> of the created tool."
msgstr ""
"Če morate v orodno vrstico dodati kakšen orodni gumb, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>. Izberete lahko <guilabel>Ime</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Vrsto</guilabel> in <guilabel>Videz</guilabel> ustvarjenega orodja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please remember that annotation tools in &okular; are highly configurable. "
"For example, you can have two buttons of the same tool but with different "
"color. Do not hesitate to experiment in choosing the button set that is "
"exactly tailored to your workflow."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite, da so orodja za opombe v &okular;ju zelo nastavljiva. Na "
"primer, lahko imate dva gumba istega orodja, vendar različnih barv. Ne "
"oklevajte in eksperimentirajte pri izbiri nabora gumbov, ki je natančno "
"prilagojen vašemu delovnemu toku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2949
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on some item in the list box then click on the corresponding button at "
"the right part of the page to edit, remove, move up or move down the item. "
"The keyboard shortcut of the tool (keys from <keycap>1</keycap> to "
"<keycap>9</keycap>) depends on its position in the list of annotation "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na določeno postavko v polju s seznamom in nato kliknite na "
"ustrezni gumb na desnem delu strani, da uredite, odstranite, premaknete "
"element navzgor ali navzdol. Bližnjica na tipkovnici orodja (tipke od "
"<keycap>1</keycap> do <keycap>9</keycap>) je odvisna od njegovega položaja "
"na seznamu orodne vrstice za opombe."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2955
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Custom Stamps"
msgstr "Uporaba žigov po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2958
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create the icon you want to use for your own stamp and save it in any "
"graphics format supported by &okular;"
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite ikono, ki jo želite uporabiti za svoj žig, in jo shranite v "
"poljubni grafični obliki, ki jo podpira &okular;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button, select type <guilabel>Stamp</"
"guilabel> and enter a name for your stamp."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>, izberite vrsto <guilabel>Žiga</"
"guilabel> in vnesite ime za svoj žig."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the full path to your custom icon into the dropdown box in the "
"<guilabel>Stamp Symbol</guilabel> group"
msgstr ""
"Vnesite celotno pot do svoje ikone po meri v spustno polje v skupini "
"<guilabel>Simbol žiga</guilabel>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2967
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Editor</title>"
msgstr "<title>Urejevalnik</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2970
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Editor</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Urejevalnik</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the editor you want to launch when &okular; wants to open a source "
"file. This is the case when the document has references to the various "
"points (usually row and column number) of sources it was generated from. The "
"&DVI; format supports natively the addition of the information about the "
"sources the &latex; document was generated from. A similar system exists for "
"&PDF; documents, called <acronym>pdfsync</acronym>, which stores these extra "
"information in an external file named after the &PDF; file itself (for "
"example <filename>mydocument.pdfsync</filename> for <filename>mydocument."
"pdf</filename>)."
msgstr ""
"Izberite urejevalnik, ki ga želite zagnati, ko želi &okular; odpreti izvorno "
"datoteko. To je v primeru, ko ima dokument sklicevanja na različne točke "
"(običajno številko vrstice in stolpca) virov, iz katerih je bil ustvarjen. "
"&DVI; format izvorno podpira dodajanje informacij o virih iz katerih je bil "
"&latex; dokument  ustvarjen. Podoben sistem obstaja za &PDF; dokumente, "
"imenovan <acronym>pdfsync</acronym>, ki te dodatne informacije shranijo v "
"zunanjo datoteko, imenovano po datoteki &PDF; sama datoteka (na primer "
"<filename>mydocument.pdfsync</filename> za <filename>mydocument.pdf</"
"filename>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2975
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&okular; ships with preconfigured settings for the following editors: <ulink "
"url=\"https://kate-editor.org/\">&kate;</ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://kile."
"sourceforge.io/\">Kile</ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://www.scintilla.org/SciTE."
"html\">SciTE</ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/"
"\">&Emacs; client</ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://www.lyx.org/\">LyX client</"
"ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://www.texstudio.org/\">TeXstudio</ulink>, and "
"<ulink url=\"https://github.com/hannah-sten/texify-idea\">TeXiFy IDEA</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&okular; pošilja s predkonfiguriranimi nastavitvami za naslednje "
"urejevalnike: <ulink url=\"https://kate-editor.org/\">&kate;</ulink>, <ulink "
"url=\"https://kile.sourceforge.io/\"> Kile</ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://www."
"scintilla.org/SciTE.html\">SciTE</ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/"
"software/emacs /\">&Emacs; odjemalec</ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://www.lyx."
"org/\">odjemalec LyX</ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://www.texstudio.org/"
"\">TeXstudio</ulink> in <ulink url=\"https://github.com/hannah-sten/texify-"
"idea\">TeXiFy IDEA</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use inverse search in &kile;, you have to compile your &latex; file with "
"the <guilabel>Modern</guilabel> configuration."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti obratno iskanje v &kile;, morate prevesti svojo &latex; "
"datoteko s konfiguracijo <guilabel>Moderno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2986
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command"
msgstr "Ukaz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the command and its parameters to invoke the selected editor with "
"the source file of the actual document."
msgstr ""
"To je ukaz in njegovi parametri za priklic izbranega urejevalnika z izvorno "
"datoteko dejanskega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2989
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This field will be filled automatically if you use one of the preconfigured "
"editors. Otherwise, please choose <guimenuitem>Custom Text Editor</"
"guimenuitem> in <guilabel>Editor</guilabel> drop down box and refer to the "
"documentation on your favorite editor to find the proper command."
msgstr ""
"To polje bo samodejno izpolnjeno, če uporabljate enega od predhodno "
"konfiguriranih urejevalnikov. V nasprotnem primeru izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Urejevalnik besedil po meri</guimenuitem> v spustnem polju "
"<guilabel>Urejevalnik</guilabel> in si oglejte dokumentacijo vašega "
"priljubljenega urejevalnika, da poiščete ustrezen ukaz."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2991
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can use the following placeholders:"
msgstr "Uporabite lahko naslednje začasne oznake:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2994
#, no-c-format
msgid "%f - the file name"
msgstr "%f - ime datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2997
#, no-c-format
msgid "%l - the line of the file to be reached"
msgstr "%l - vrstica datoteke, ki jo želite doseči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3000
#, no-c-format
msgid "%c - the column of the file to be reached"
msgstr "%c - stolpec datoteke, ki jo želite doseči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3003
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If %f is not specified, then the document name is appended to the specified "
"command."
msgstr "Če %f ni podan, je podanemu ukazu dodano ime dokumenta."

